(221, 7459, 'Speed Racer', 'Go!', 2008, 'Speed Racer is the tale of a young and brilliant racing driver. When corruption in the racing leagues costs his brother his life, he must team up with the police and the mysterious Racer X to bring an end to the corruption and criminal activities. Inspired by the cartoon series.', 5.7, 17.060696, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fxRIpx9Op9h71q3tvuabx4GryyP.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E_uB9nrFfSo'),
