(223, 37834, 'Knight and Day', 'Every Hit Man Deserves a Second Shot!', 2010, 'A fugitive couple goes on a glamorous and sometimes deadly adventure where nothing and no one – even themselves – are what they seem. Amid shifting alliances and unexpected betrayals, they race across the globe, with their survival ultimately hinging on the battle of truth vs. trust.', 5.9, 44.906918, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/phhp52CZZJiGYmiOTp9ZBDkGHB3.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VDoNfrBlY3o'),
(224, 75612, 'Oblivion', 'Earth is a memory worth fighting for', 2013, 'Jack Harper is one of the last few drone repairmen stationed on Earth.  Part of a massive operation to extract vital resources after decades of war with a terrifying threat known as the Scavs, Jack’s mission is nearly complete.  His existence is brought crashing down when he rescues a beautiful  stranger from a downed spacecraft.  Her arrival triggers a chain of events that  forces him to question everything he knows and puts the fate of humanity in his hands.', 6.4, 67.698006, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/eO3r38fwnhb58M1YgcjQBd3VNcp.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tx6_JMDFfWI'),
(225, 1895, 'Star Wars: Episode III - Revenge of the Sith', 'The saga is complete.', 2005, 'Years after the onset of the Clone Wars, the noble Jedi Knights lead a massive clone army into a galaxy-wide battle against the Separatists. When the sinister Sith unveil a thousand-year-old plot to rule the galaxy, the Republic crumbles and from its ashes rises the evil Galactic Empire. Jedi hero Anakin Skywalker is seduced by the dark side of the Force to become the Emperor''s new apprentice – Darth Vader. The Jedi are decimated, as Obi-Wan Kenobi and Jedi Master Yoda are forced into hiding. The only hope for the galaxy are Anakin''s own offspring – the twin children born in secrecy who will grow up to become heroes.', 7.1, 44.108425, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xfSAoBEm9MNBjmlNcDYLvLSMlnq.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5UnjrG_N8hU'),
(226, 1894, 'Star Wars: Episode II - Attack of the Clones', 'A Jedi Shall Not Know Anger. Nor Hatred. Nor Love.', 2002, 'Ten years after the invasion of Naboo, the galaxy is on the brink of civil war. Under the leadership of a renegade Jedi named Count Dooku, thousands of solar systems threaten to break away from the Galactic Republic. When an assassination attempt is made on Senator Padmé Amidala, the former Queen of Naboo, twenty-year-old Jedi apprentice Anakin Skywalker is assigned to protect her. In the course of his mission, Anakin discovers his love for Padmé as well as his own darker side. Soon, Anakin, Padmé, and Obi-Wan Kenobi are drawn into the heart of the Separatist movement and the beginning of the Clone Wars.', 6.4, 43.98706, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oZNPzxqM2s5DyVWab09NTQScDQt.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lG8k-DkGfT4'),
(227, 585, 'Monsters, Inc.', 'We Scare Because We Care.', 2001, 'James Sullivan and Mike Wazowski are monsters, they earn their living scaring children and are the best in the business... even though they''re more afraid of the children than they are of them. When a child accidentally enters their world, James and Mike suddenly find that kids are not to be afraid of and they uncover a conspiracy that could threaten all children across the world.', 7.5, 106.815544, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qjlbN6aK1qgeg3SspFVovT2D1Me.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GnuQH_ASzu8'),
(228, 76170, 'The Wolverine', 'When he''s most vulnerable, he''s most dangerous.', 2013, 'Wolverine faces his ultimate nemesis - and tests of his physical, emotional, and mortal limits - in a life-changing voyage to modern-day Japan.', 6.3, 15.953444, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8lzmovtARDXnE7kTDOum02i6fXv.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DwG56k6VGOE'),
(229, 1893, 'Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace', 'Every generation has a legend. Every journey has a first step. Every saga has a beginning.', 1999, 'Anakin Skywalker, a young slave strong with the Force, is discovered on Tatooine. Meanwhile, the evil Sith have returned, enacting their plot for revenge against the Jedi.', 6.3, 54.035267, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6wkfovpn7Eq8dYNKaG5PY3q2oq6.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J3kyYFHdRsM'),
(230, 49519, 'The Croods', 'Meet the first modern family.', 2013, 'The Croods is a prehistoric comedy adventure that follows the world''s first family as they embark on a journey of a lifetime when the cave that has always shielded them from danger is destroyed. Traveling across a spectacular landscape, the Croods discover an incredible new world filled with fantastic creatures -- and their outlook is changed forever.', 6.8, 64.18332, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/27zvjVOtOi5ped1HSlJKNsKXkFH.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E80GplS1OG8'),
(231, 2395, 'Asterix at the Olympic Games', '', 2008, 'Astérix and Obélix have to win the Olympic Games in order to help their friend Alafolix marry Princess Irina (portrayed by supermodel Vanessa Hessler). Brutus (Benoît Poelvoorde) uses every trick in the book to have his own team win the game, and get rid of his father Julius Caesar (Alain Delon) in the process.', 5, 20.344364, 'fr', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/eNB2SrqmTJLByRDq3akDzA6Z9rC.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I4IwYe5N1o0'),
(232, 12100, 'Windtalkers', 'Honor Was Their Code.', 2002, 'Joe Enders is a gung-ho Marine assigned to protect a "windtalker" - one of several Navajo Indians who were used to relay messages during World War II because their spoken language was indecipherable to Japanese code breakers.', 5.8, 18.714197, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/547q4HXlvEcS06lujfb2yzsTP3H.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BfI-vfxEN3U'),
(233, 290595, 'The Huntsman: Winter''s War', 'The story before Snow White', 2016, 'As two evil sisters prepare to conquer the land, two renegades—Eric the Huntsman, who aided Snow White in defeating Ravenna in Snowwhite and the Huntsman, and his forbidden lover, Sara—set out to stop them.', 6, 60.467983, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ci1QXfBSUBVpLuzxi9A208uwUVi.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V9cPxenX1-0'),
(234, 98566, 'Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles', 'Mysterious. Dangerous. Reptilious. You''ve never seen heroes like this.', 2014, 'The city needs heroes. Darkness has settled over New York City as Shredder and his evil Foot Clan have an iron grip on everything from the police to the politicians. The future is grim until four unlikely outcast brothers rise from the sewers and discover their destiny as Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles. The Turtles must work with fearless reporter April and her wise-cracking cameraman Vern Fenwick to save the city and unravel Shredder''s diabolical plan.', 5.8, 143.35037, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/azL2ThbJMIkts3ZMt3j1YgBUeDB.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dwXFsrp6WBs'),
(235, 49047, 'Gravity', 'Don''t Let Go', 2013, 'Dr. Ryan Stone, a brilliant medical engineer on her first Shuttle mission, with veteran astronaut Matt Kowalsky in command of his last flight before retiring. But on a seemingly routine spacewalk, disaster strikes. The Shuttle is destroyed, leaving Stone and Kowalsky completely alone-tethered to nothing but each other and spiraling out into the blackness of space. The deafening silence tells them they have lost any link to Earth and any chance for rescue. As fear turns to panic, every gulp of air eats away at what little oxygen is left. But the only way home may be to go further out into the terrifying expanse of space.', 7.3, 110.15362, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kZ2nZw8D681aphje8NJi8EfbL1U.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OiTiKOy59o4'),
(236, 9619, 'Dante''s Peak', 'The pressure is building...', 1997, 'Volcanologist Harry Dalton comes to the sleepy town of Dante''s Peak to investigate the recent rumblings of the dormant volcano the burg is named for. Before long, his worst fears are realized when a massive eruption hits, and immediately, Harry, the mayor and the townspeople find themselves fighting for their lives amid a catastrophic nightmare.', 5.7, 16.90444, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8PRVIfZzDgw8EV3sDWJ6NA1ZMAn.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p_oFoX3GniA'),
(237, 308531, 'Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Out of the Shadows', 'Raise some shell.', 2016, 'After supervillain Shredder escapes custody, he joins forces with mad scientist Baxter Stockman and two dimwitted henchmen, Bebop and Rocksteady, to unleash a diabolical plan to take over the world. As the Turtles prepare to take on Shredder and his new crew, they find themselves facing an even greater evil with similar intentions: the notorious Krang.', 5.8, 39.87379, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/euVaCiCWz3AALcQXHT6aUqdGUo6.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ubursnjg8NA'),
(238, 166424, 'Fantastic Four', 'Change is coming.', 2015, 'Four young outsiders teleport to a dangerous universe, which alters their physical form in shocking ways. Their lives irrevocably upended, the team must learn to harness their daunting new abilities and work together to save Earth from a former friend turned enemy.', 4.4, 38.126095, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oeMpEsjmiT9PEJbRM1Fm7TZ1dE0.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AAgnQdiZFsQ'),
(239, 1593, 'Night at the Museum', 'Where History Comes To Life', 2006, 'Chaos reigns at the natural history museum when night watchman Larry Daley accidentally stirs up an ancient curse, awakening Attila the Hun, an army of gladiators, a Tyrannosaurus rex and other exhibits. Larry tries desperately to keep the museum under control, but he''s fighting a losing battle until President Teddy Roosevelt comes to the rescue.', 6.3, 48.78004, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pDsAAYf6Zn0yiAGJ6lYGs6hoZ4E.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ltba1_-tRT4'),
(240, 254128, 'San Andreas', 'A rescue pilot survived an earthquake, this is what happens next', 2015, 'In the aftermath of a massive earthquake in California, a rescue-chopper pilot makes a dangerous journey across the state in order to rescue his estranged daughter.', 6, 100.41236, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2Gfjn962aaFSD6eST6QU3oLDZTo.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F1ZewAPl7L0'),
(241, 714, 'Tomorrow Never Dies', 'Yesterday is a memory. Today is history. Tomorrow is in the hands of one man.', 1997, 'A deranged media mogul is staging international incidents to pit the world''s superpowers against each other. Now 007 must take on this evil mastermind in an adrenaline-charged battle to end his reign of terror and prevent global pandemonium.', 6, 42.88712, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gZm002w7q9yLOkltxT76TWGfdZX.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QP1FMpIo-uQ'),
(242, 2024, 'The Patriot', 'Some things are worth fighting for.', 2000, 'After proving himself on the field of battle in the French and Indian War, Benjamin Martin wants nothing more to do with such things, preferring the simple life of a farmer. But when his son Gabriel enlists in the army to defend their new nation, America, against the British, Benjamin reluctantly returns to his old life to protect his son.', 6.8, 23.657284, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fWZd815QxUCUcrWQZwUkAp9ljG.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OpKR4qTOVgI'),
(243, 163, 'Ocean''s Twelve', 'Twelve is the new eleven.', 2004, 'Danny Ocean reunites with his old flame and the rest of his merry band of thieves in carrying out three huge heists in Rome, Paris and Amsterdam – but a Europol agent is hot on their heels.', 6.4, 76.84071, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pE5anFf7nf6ah7V3VRezQ1KSovi.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ATHwwFhB-UQ'),
(244, 787, 'Mr. & Mrs. Smith', 'Smart and sexy.', 2005, 'After five (or six) years of vanilla-wedded bliss, ordinary suburbanites John and Jane Smith are stuck in a huge rut. Unbeknownst to each other, they are both coolly lethal, highly-paid assassins working for rival organisations. When they discover they''re each other''s next target, their secret lives collide in a spicy, explosive mix of wicked comedy, pent-up passion, nonstop action and high-tech weaponry.', 6.5, 44.635452, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kjD700RtyhveN3ZbOnSvUSne0Qj.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TWB_icm5M38'),
