(246, 2567, 'The Aviator', 'For some men, the sky was the limit. For him, it was just the beginning.', 2004, 'A biopic depicting the life of filmmaker and aviation pioneer Howard Hughes from 1927 to 1947, during which time he became a successful film producer and an aviation magnate, while simultaneously growing more unstable due to severe obsessive-compulsive disorder.', 7, 45.616096, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lx4kWcZc3o9PaNxlQpEJZM17XUI.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dkwypzOQf8o'),
