(264, 10137, 'Stuart Little', 'The Little Family Just Got Bigger', 1999, 'The adventures of a heroic and debonair stalwart mouse named Stuart Little with human qualities, who faces some comic misadventures while searching for his lost bird friend and living with a human family as their child.', 5.8, 30.475298, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/362lcwTJlNyAhitTlp2UraECISR.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Wlo-sYrADlw'),
