(544, 8688, 'Snake Eyes', 'Believe everything except your eyes.', 1998, 'All bets are off when corrupt homicide cop Rick Santoro witnesses a murder during a boxing match. It''s up to him and lifelong friend and naval intelligence agent Kevin Dunne to uncover the conspiracy behind the killing. At every turn, Santoro makes increasingly shocking discoveries that even he can''t turn a blind eye to.', 5.8, 20.790703, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kdcLZmZdEWeuqJ4ed68CL7Bcd2R.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LwNgUdp2otk'),
(545, 10153, 'Sphere', 'A thousand feet beneath the sea, the blackest holes are in the mind...', 1998, 'The OSSA discovers a spacecraft thought to be at least 300 years old at the bottom of the ocean. Immediately following the discovery, they decide to send a team down to the depths of the ocean to study the space craft.They are the best of best, smart and logical, and the perfect choice to learn more about the spacecraft.', 5.8, 18.65988, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5IMr0L4BoONvN5i9kyVd0zGww3L.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dz9LvCAOoDA'),
(546, 153518, 'The Angry Birds Movie', 'Why so angry?', 2016, 'An island populated entirely by happy, flightless birds or almost entirely. In this paradise, Red, a bird with a temper problem, speedy Chuck, and the volatile Bomb have always been outsiders. But when the island is visited by mysterious green piggies, it’s up to these unlikely outcasts to figure out what the pigs are up to.', 5.9, 45.720894, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/iOH0fEFtV9z9rZp9zmBFGGeWicv.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Hksyh33N5dg'),
