(548, 20829, 'Funny People', 'George Simmons was prepared to die, but then a funny thing happened.', 2009, 'Famous and wealthy funnyman George Simmons doesn''t give much thought to how he treats people until a doctor delivers stunning health news, forcing George to reevaluate his priorities with a little help from aspiring stand-up comic Ira.', 5.7, 20.199057, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gEYKD5cWCBGg8Za3hhwDBk3gEsP.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gMhMQuOIWiQ'),
