(550, 9718, 'Talladega Nights: The Ballad of Ricky Bobby', 'The story of a man who could only count to #1', 2006, 'Lifelong friends and national idols Ricky Bobby and Cal Naughton Jr. have earned their NASCAR stripes with their uncanny knack of finishing races in the first and second slots, respectively, and slinging catchphrases like "Shake and bake!" But when a rival French driver coasts onto the track to challenge their records, they''ll have to floor it to retain their top-dog status.', 6.2, 12.599836, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/drLHIv8NUdaXOWapQhleECrtrcW.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Kc9Xty70x00'),
(551, 10808, 'Dr. Dolittle 2', 'The doctor is in again.', 2001, 'Dr. John Dolittle the beloved doctor is back, but this time around he plays cupid to bumbling circus bear Archie as he''s so smitten by a Pacific Western bear female, Ava. Dr. Dolittle must help a group of forest creatures to save their forest. But with the aid of his mangy, madcap animal friends, Dr. Dolittle must teach Archie the ways of true romance in time to save his species and his home before their habit is gone. So John held a meeting for every animal in the forest to not give up without a fight no matter what kind of animal expression they have and everyone agrees to do it and save their home.', 4.9, 13.543053, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/asYjHXBoD44B6mLOcZtMfMV3hm1.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EXpnizX4kMA'),
