(581, 57212, 'War Horse', 'Separated by War. Tested by Battle. Bound by Friendship.', 2011, 'Follows a young man named Albert and his horse, Joey, and how their bond is broken when Joey is sold to the cavalry and sent to the trenches of World War One. Despite being too young to enlist, Albert heads to France to save his friend.', 7, 29.505573, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3aRHhvvngFPJFy5uAjo7GVr3PhL.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kEhmx28Tbek'),
(582, 152760, 'The Monuments Men', 'It was the greatest art heist in history', 2014, 'Based on the true story of the greatest treasure hunt in history, The Monuments Men is an action drama focusing on seven over-the-hill, out-of-shape museum directors, artists, architects, curators, and art historians who went to the front lines of WWII to rescue the world’s artistic masterpieces from Nazi thieves and return them to their rightful owners.  With the art hidden behind enemy lines, how could these guys hope to succeed?', 5.8, 43.873264, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wiWAg4mKV2S4vImPxsPRIdj2R2B.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oBfMOmR4S9M'),
(583, 2756, 'The Abyss', 'There''s everything you''ve ever known about adventure, and then there''s The Abyss.', 1989, 'A civilian oil rig crew is recruited to conduct a search and rescue effort when a nuclear submarine mysteriously sinks. One diver soon finds himself on a spectacular odyssey 25,000 feet below the ocean''s surface where he confronts a mysterious force that has the power to change the world or destroy it.', 7.1, 24.961624, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2dCit3XAtv9KWCJvRKdPkJ0FAkH.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7cCVYAcIIAo'),
