(593, 52520, 'Underworld: Awakening', 'Vengeance Returns', 2012, 'After being held in a coma-like state for fifteen years, vampire Selene learns that she has a fourteen-year-old vampire/Lycan hybrid daughter named Nissa, and when she finds her, they must stop BioCom from creating super Lycans that will kill them all.', 6.1, 58.401203, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jN0uuc8U6M3sTg9zEaliJV60Stf.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tUcrbUCWKQc'),
