(1091, 1494, 'Curse of the Golden Flower', 'Unspeakable secrets are hidden within the Forbidden City.', 2006, 'During China''s Tang dynasty the emperor has taken the princess of a neighboring province as wife. She has borne him two sons and raised his eldest. Now his control over his dominion is complete, including the royal family itself.', 6.6, 9.950505, 'zh', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gHkkDpfo5YnOrbVfwtDHi91BkrU.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c-W5dl98ZWA'),
(1092, 13184, 'Bangkok Dangerous', 'There''s only one way out.', 2008, 'When carrying out a hit, assassin Joe (Cage) always makes use of the knowledge of the local population. On arriving in Bangkok, Joe meets street kid Kong and he becomes his primary aide. But when Kong is nearly killed, he asks Joe to train him up in the deadly arts and unwittingly becomes a target of a band of killers.', 5, 14.813057, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/iTRftxHW8i4H7ONaOiCIwEXjNDJ.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e_b2QVAVRpc'),
(1093, 2185, 'Big Trouble', 'They have forty-five minutes to save the world. They need forty-six.', 2002, 'The story of how a mysterious suitcase brings together, and changes, the lives of a divorced dad, an unhappy housewife, two hitmen, a pair of street thugs, two love struck teens, two FBI men and a psychedelic toad. Based on Pulitzer Prize-winning humorist Dave Barry''s best-selling first novel, "Big Trouble."', 6.3, 5.201688, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/h844gBztdYMLrroUen6qbsomrGx.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=os-iPdjKgMs'),
(1094, 6639, 'Love in the Time of Cholera', 'How long would you wait for love?', 2007, 'In Colombia just after the Great War, an old man falls from a ladder; dying, he professes great love for his wife. After the funeral, a man calls on the widow - she dismisses him angrily. Flash back more than 50 years to the day Florentino Ariza, a telegraph boy, falls in love with Fermina Daza, the daughter of a mule trader.', 6.4, 5.361699, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7y5VuS218Nqc8eVdeuOrlYWWD0D.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KkDpvgncboQ'),
(1095, 38153, 'Shadow Conspiracy', '', 1997, 'Bobby Bishop (Sheen) is a special assistant to the President of the United States. Accidentally, he meets his friend professor Pochenko on the street. Pochenko has time to tell Bishop about some conspiracy in the White House but then immediately gets killed by an assassin. Now bad guys are after Bobby as the only man who knows about a plot. Bishop must now not only survive, but to stop the conspirators from achieving their goal. And he doesn''t know whom to trust.', 4, 3.848893, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/m8dgxxCrpLhKjkjH2DPxkz0inoJ.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U2CNeff1Q5M'),
(1096, 58233, 'Johnny English Reborn', 'One man. One mission. No chance.', 2011, 'The most prominent heads of state in the world begin gathering for a conference that could have a major impact on global politics. When MI-7 receives word that the Chinese premier has become the target of some high-powered killers, it falls on Johnny English to save the day. Armed with the latest high-tech weaponry and gadgets that would make even James Bond jealous, the once-disgraced agent uncovers evidence of a massive conspiracy involving some of the world''s most powerful organisations, and vows to redeem his tarnished reputation by stopping the killers before they can strike.', 6, 35.6585, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zDbrU0eSnRGh5gHc1iqTACTNNyT.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wCsSzZU-sQ4'),
