(1120, 136795, 'The Heat', 'Action''s never been so hot!', 2013, 'Uptight and straight-laced, FBI Special Agent Sarah Ashburn is a methodical investigator with a reputation for excellence--and hyper-arrogance. Shannon Mullins, one of Boston P.D.''s "finest," is foul-mouthed and has a very short fuse, and uses her gut instinct and street smarts to catch the most elusive criminals. Neither has ever had a partner, or a friend for that matter. When these two wildly incompatible law officers join forces to bring down a ruthless drug lord, they become the last thing anyone expected: Buddies.', 6.5, 37.65469, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/yERBa1y5zNUOTRKQPiDCPIc2fuv.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1O3iRdiplB0'),
