(1412, 9541, 'Jersey Girl', 'He wanted it all...but he got more than he bargained for.', 2004, 'Ollie Trinke is a young, suave music publicist who seems to have it all, with a new wife and a baby on the way. But life deals him a bum hand when he''s suddenly faced with single fatherhood, a defunct career and having to move in with his father. To bounce back, it takes a new love and the courage instilled in him by his daughter.', 5.8, 14.699342, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/nMmMWoSooR6QmCjdT0AvZardof1.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CL04A-DrIEQ'),
(1413, 94348, 'Alex Cross', 'Don''t Ever Cross Alex Cross', 2012, 'After Washington DC detective Alex Cross is told that a family member has been murdered, he vows to track down the killer. He soon discovers that she was not his first victim and that things are not what they seem.', 5.1, 14.513243, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bQYXid9o6nunJBgmmjo6JFIQe1p.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Uw7PhPD31Ws'),
