(1432, 35169, 'Furry Vengeance', 'He came. He saw. They conquered.', 2010, 'When real estate developer Dan Sanders finalizes plans to level a swath of pristine Oregon forest to make way for a soulless housing subdivision, a band of woodland creatures rises up to throw a monkey wrench into the greedy scheme. Just how much mischief from the furry critters can the businessman take before he calls it quits?', 4.6, 13.668633, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/604qqquWBgFy34jLhHLtebFPQy6.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FQAx4_So3UE'),
