(1435, 4515, 'Lions for Lambs', 'If you don''t STAND for something, you might FALL for anything.', 2007, 'Three stories told simultaneous in ninety minutes of real time: a Republican Senator who''s a presidential hopeful gives an hour-long interview to a skeptical television reporter, detailing a strategy for victory in Afghanistan; two special forces ambushed on an Afghani ridge await rescue as Taliban forces close in; a poli-sci professor at a California college invites a student to re-engage.', 6, 9.789027, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rvpxNsR0n4zh40WM6MiUlkV60on.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n_V6ulwA0KE'),
(1436, 18886, 'Flight of the Intruder', 'The only thing they can count on is each other.', 1991, 'U.S. Navy pilot Lt. Jake Grafton and his bombardier buddy, Lt. Cmdr. Virgil Cole, are two soldiers embedded in the Vietnam War growing frustrated by the military''s constraints on their missions. Despite the best efforts of their commanding officer, Cmdr. Frank Camparelli, to re-engage them, this disillusioned pair decide to take the war effort into their own hands with an explosive battle plan that could well get them court-martialed.', 5.7, 6.81729, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tzjCePBItSRfZxLnOd3KBGHQIJl.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jg0s5ljjShQ'),
