(1438, 6440, 'The Shipping News', 'You''ll never guess what you''ll find inside...', 2001, 'An emotionally-beaten man with his young daughter moves to his ancestral home in Newfoundland to reclaim his life.', 6.4, 11.1399, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3IdEZw4YN4NfvjLRyZVWpI0z2IH.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8x1z8IK-L0U'),
(1439, 13496, 'American Outlaws', 'Sometimes the wrong side of the law is the right place to be.', 2001, 'When a Midwest town learns that a corrupt railroad baron has captured the deeds to their homesteads without their knowledge, a group of young ranchers join forces to take back what is rightfully theirs. They will become the object of the biggest manhunt in the history of the Old West and, as their fame grows, so will the legend of their leader, a young outlaw by the name of Jessie James.', 5.7, 6.727949, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bfHkHstHIBpDAokujviWZw3mL8M.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tJMUjVG6ZRg'),
(1440, 18320, 'The Young Victoria', 'Love rules all.', 2009, 'From Academy Award® winners Graham King and Martin Scorsese, along with the makers of Gosford Park and The Departed, comes the story of Queen Victoria’s early rise to power. From an object of a royal power-struggle to her romantic courtship and legendary marriage to Prince Albert, Emily Blunt (The Devil Wears Prada) gives a stunning performance as the young Victoria. Packed with drama, romance, breath-taking cinematography, lavish costumes and featuring an outstanding British cast including Jim Broadbent, Harriet Walter, Mark Strong, Paul Bettany, Miranda Richardson, and Rupert Friend, The Young Victoria has captivated British audiences, and is the film that Company magazine called “an epic British film, which will sweep you up in her remarkable story.”', 7, 16.343317, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pkt58GhSPBd7vvnZFIiu2IgbwSk.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q-YPoBU7_aQ'),
(1441, 22787, 'Whiteout', 'See Your Last Breath', 2009, 'The only U.S. Marshal assigned to Antarctica, Carrie Stetko will soon leave the harsh environment behind for good – in three days, the sun will set and the Amundsen-Scott Research Station will shut down for the long winter. When a body is discovered out on the open ice, Carrie''s investigation into the continent''s first homicide plunges her deep into a mystery that may cost her her own life.', 5.3, 14.818718, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kkXXA3353MX60B8PRSkTGRabxXu.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GqxjF9qR5Cg'),
(1442, 8967, 'The Tree of Life', 'Nothing stands still.', 2011, 'The impressionistic story of a Texas family in the 1950s. The film follows the life journey of the eldest son, Jack, through the innocence of childhood to his disillusioned adult years as he tries to reconcile a complicated relationship with his father. Jack finds himself a lost soul in the modern world, seeking answers to the origins and meaning of life while questioning the existence of faith.', 6.5, 43.862457, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/l8cwuB5WJSoj4uMAsnzuHBOMaSJ.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RrAz1YLh8nY'),
(1443, 37498, 'Knock Off', 'There is no substitute.', 1998, 'Marcus Ray (Jean-Claude Van Damme), a sales representative for "V SIX" jeans, and his partner, Tommy Hendricks (Rob Schneider), are about to be busted for selling "knock off" jeans. Their American contact, Karan Leigh, who by the way is not only their employer but a CIA agent sent to find the mole in their operation, is threatening them with a jail term if they do not prove their innocence.', 4.7, 2.706207, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hK7hKDA51FCbtFCuXZNiQ6gPq3S.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5Txm_I4usB0'),
(1444, 144336, 'Sabotage', 'Leave no loose ends', 2014, 'In "Sabotage", Arnold Schwarzenegger leads an elite DEA task force that takes on the world''s deadliest drug cartels. When the team successfully executes a high-stakes raid on a cartel safe house, they think their work is done - until, one-by-one, the team members mysteriously start to be eliminated. As the body count rises, everyone is a suspect.', 5.5, 27.904, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ygG17WukZCidKm7wGM3Zzrr5WRi.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8HDArXZgrsE'),
(1445, 9616, 'The Order', 'Every soul has its price.', 2003, 'For centuries, a secret Order of priests has existed within the Church. A renegade priest, Father Alex Bernier, is sent to Rome to investigate the mysterious death of one of the Order''s most revered members. Following a series of strangely similar killings, Bernier launches an investigation that forces him to confront unimaginable evil.', 4.8, 3.746806, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7kj4TffoKCt4gIrNupr2oqmir69.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yHi8YN0sz6I'),
(1446, 13056, 'Punisher: War Zone', 'Vengeance has a name', 2008, 'Waging his one-man war on the world of organized crime, ruthless vigilante-hero Frank Castle sets his sights on overeager mob boss Billy Russoti. After Russoti is left horribly disfigured by Castle, he sets out for vengeance under his new alias: Jigsaw. With the "Punisher Task Force" hot on his trail and the FBI unable to take Jigsaw in, Frank must stand up to the formidable army that Jigsaw has recruited before more of his evil deeds go unpunished.', 5.6, 17.112497, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oOvKJgYUIpfswGHAdW6159bPbvM.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=liABMxEvPAc'),
(1447, 14113, 'Zoom', 'They''re going to save the world... as long as they''re home for dinner.', 2006, 'Jack Shepard is an out-of-shape auto shop owner, far removed from the man who once protected the world''s freedom. Reluctantly called back into action by the government, Jack is tasked with turning a rag tag group of kids with special powers into a new generation of superheroes to save the world from certain destruction. Based on Jason Lethcoe''s graphic novel "Zoom''s Academy for the Super Gifted".', 4.9, 10.304172, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/v4rSFmiy0v9D7qmKkaUVJn5UhZ1.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5y7q5b3WyEc'),
(1448, 285783, 'The Walk', 'Dream High.', 2015, 'The story of French high-wire artist Philippe Petit''s attempt to cross the Twin Towers of the World Trade Center in 1974.', 6.9, 37.33572, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tiESRqurrZwAC0hpERogOsBhjeg.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4W6byFcD5uE'),
(1449, 49478, 'Warriors of Virtue', 'In a world beyond your imagination a battle for the universe has begun.', 1997, 'A young man, Ryan, suffering from a disability, wishes to join the other kids from his schools football team. During an initiation rite, Ryan is swept away through a whirlpool to the land of Tao. There he is hunted by the evil Lord Komodo, who desires the boy as a key to enter the real world. Ryan is rescued by the protectors of Tao, five humanoid kangaroos, each embued with the five elements and virtues. Ryan learns his valuable lesson while saving the land of Tao.', 4.7, 0.912395, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8fT8cttGyXx36P24W0tum2QxsLf.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-4STNypFBh0'),
(1450, 9726, 'A Good Year', 'Everything matures... eventually.', 2006, 'Failed London banker Max Skinner inherits his uncle''s vineyard in Provence, where he spent many childhood holidays. Upon his arrival, he meets a woman from California who tells Max she is his long-lost cousin and that the property is hers.', 6.5, 16.78247, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2Kn73vimhOjLaPZFoI0IDUT5RtK.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bKKrLj5ZHiM'),
(1451, 20763, 'Radio Flyer', 'Powered by imagination.', 1992, 'A father reminisces about his childhood when he and his younger brother moved to a new town with their mother, her new husband and their dog, Shane. When the younger brother is subjected to physical abuse at the hands of their brutal stepfather, Mike decides to convert their toy trolley, the "Radio Flyer", into a plane to fly him to safety.', 6.6, 3.503408, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/nQjCKrwWYH6ES0HrnkLkPXnOEp0.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gxsfeyl5g7I'),
(1452, 9702, 'Bound by Honor', 'An epic story of three brothers. Bound by blood. Divided by fate. Driven by destiny.', 1993, 'Based on the true life experiences of poet Jimmy Santiago Baca, the film focuses on half-brothers Paco and Cruz, and their bi-racial cousin Miklo. It opens in 1972, as the three are members of an East L.A. gang known as the "Vatos Locos", and the story focuses on how a violent crime and the influence of narcotics alter their lives. Miklo is incarcerated and sent to San Quentin, where he makes a "home" for himself. Cruz becomes an exceptional artist, but a heroin addiction overcomes him with tragic results. Paco becomes a cop and an enemy to his "carnal", Miklo.', 7.7, 9.122828, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gvP6R6juhe2IpCG7QGDgjyUvm0g.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NMj89zgI8Yc'),
(1453, 9311, 'Smilla''s Sense of Snow', 'Some Tracks Should Never Be Uncovered.', 1997, 'Smilla Jaspersen, half Danish, half Greenlander, attempts to understand the death of a small boy who falls from the roof of her apartment building. Suspecting wrongdoing, Smilla uncovers a trail of clues leading towards a secretive corporation that has made several mysterious expeditions to Greenland. Scenes from the film were shot in Copenhagen and western Greenland. The film was entered into the 47th Berlin International Film Festival, where director Bille August was nominated for the Golden Bear.', 6.6, 5.419181, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3eeCYGVWb4Ic8SFpARGWOjyl9Md.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sr7svnup0Dk'),
(1454, 9280, 'Femme Fatale', 'Nothing is more desirable or more deadly than a woman with a secret.', 2002, 'A woman tries to straighten out her life, even as her past as a con-woman comes back to haunt her.', 6.2, 9.07278, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/i2OgxmZVbIsJxaLiYMjCSewsLty.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I9xLOMw-jb8'),
(1455, 26843, 'Lion of the Desert', 'He was a man of honor in a war without any.', 1981, 'This movie tells the story of Omar Mukhtar, an Arab Muslim rebel who fought against the Italian conquest of Libya in WWII. It gives western viewers a glimpse into this little-known region and chapter of history, and exposes the savage means by which the conquering army attempted to subdue the natives.', 7.4, 2.864979, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xm7CKN5mo09RNAcL1IP1xmJ5avT.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s_lpj5k0TnU'),
(1456, 11876, 'The Horseman on the Roof', '', 1995, 'In a time of war and disease, a young officer gallantly tries to help a young woman find her husband.', 6.7, 2.877488, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tsmwnxi8hGXQTNVqBRCAVsfeGON.jpg', NULL),
(1457, 22267, 'Ride with the Devil', 'In a No-man''s Land between North and South, You didn''t fight for the Blue or the Grey... You fought for your friends and family.', 1999, 'Ride with the Devil follows four people who are fighting for truth and justice amidst the turmoil of the American Civil War. Director Ang Lee takes us to a no man''s land on the Missouri/Kansas border where a staunch loyalist, an immigrant''s son, a freed slave, and a young widow form an unlikely friendship as they learn how to survive in an uncertain time. In a place without rules and redefine the meaning of bravery and honor.', 6.6, 5.516207, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pH3J5IUzho4ZVaRuTuErzqHHovb.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F8Vwm6dBQI8'),
(1458, 45958, 'Biutiful', 'You don''t choose your family. We all belong to somebody, but to belong to Uxbal and Marambra, is both a blessing and a curse.', 2010, 'This is a story of a man in free fall. On the road to redemption, darkness lights his way. Connected with the afterlife, Uxbal is a tragic hero and father of two who''s sensing the danger of death. He struggles with a tainted reality and a fate that works against him in order to forgive, for love, and forever.', 7, 13.930763, 'es', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4BLshBMp8INRDhvfuKwxMlHDIIt.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ygyeEOcKGWM'),
(1459, 1969, 'Bandidas', 'Being BAD never looked so GOOD!', 2006, 'Set in the late 19th century. When a ruthless robber baron takes away everything they cherish, a rough-and-tumble, idealistic peasant and a sophisticated heiress embark on a quest for justice, vengeance…and a few good heists.', 5.8, 20.27704, 'es', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8aIYVBPI5Ld81I4tcHkvzoUoCEy.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gEoz9mpxBVg'),
(1460, 310706, 'Black Water Transit', '', 2009, 'In this action thriller set in post-Katrina New Orleans, business owner Jack Vermillion (Laurence Fishburne) is struggling to run a legitimate shipping company while bad guy Ernest Pike (Karl Urban) is struggling to get his family''s illegal gun collection out of the country. When their paths collide, Jack realizes that exposing Pike might get him just the sway he needs to persuade law enforcement officials to treat his imprisoned son kindly.', 0, 0.126738, 'en', NULL, NULL),
(1461, 198663, 'The Maze Runner', 'Run - Remember - Survive', 2014, 'Set in a post-apocalyptic world, young Thomas is deposited in a community of boys after his memory is erased, soon learning they''re all trapped in a maze that will require him to join forces with fellow "runners" for a shot at escape.', 7, 131.81558, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ode14q7WtDugFDp78fo9lCsmay9.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3b946aGm0zs'),
(1462, 239573, 'Unfinished Business', 'Best business trip ever.', 2015, 'A hard-working small business owner and his two associates travel to Europe to close the most important deal of their lives.  But what began as a routine business trip goes off the rails in every imaginable – and unimaginable – way, including unplanned stops at a massive sex fetish event and a global economic summit.', 5, 16.832312, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/eVWVZf3fkx9eNqbHyn9xNlmC2h4.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8yb9Dn2mnMg'),
(1463, 10436, 'The Age of Innocence', 'In a world of tradition. In an age of innocence. They dared to break the rules.', 1993, 'Tale of 19th century New York high society in which a young lawyer falls in love with a woman separated from her husband, while he is engaged to the woman''s cousin.', 7, 9.133747, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5Tuyt26v7qNR8Cl3m7ZRx36rduf.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I3Mx8OSlNYM'),
(1464, 1381, 'The Fountain', 'Death is the road to awe', 2006, 'Spanning over one thousand years, and three parallel stories, The Fountain is a story of love, death, spirituality, and the fragility of our existence in this world.', 6.8, 24.606012, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4ZZX5hqdnWtR64LkjUGBhzNabce.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pT1B1ykme2M'),
(1465, 2162, 'Chill Factor', 'This Fall, Action is served on the rocks, with a twist.', 1999, 'A store clerk and an ice cream truck driver are thrown together when a dying scientist entrusts them with a deadly chemical kept in ice. This chemical will kill every living thing once it melts. They have to take the chemical codenamed ''Elvis'' to the next nearest military base while being chased by terrorists who want it to hold the country for ransom.', 5.3, 3.276912, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/t8Qn1iKnvVOttEqaj6hz9tKGBjD.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CnsDlSoSvEo'),
(1466, 127493, 'Stolen', 'Never steal from the world''s greatest thief.', 2012, 'A former thief frantically searches for his missing daughter, who has been kidnapped and locked in the trunk of a taxi.', 5.1, 16.830185, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8rTcpPiet2Lt2uZXBFIH5U7ylBY.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7T4cYMrmsC0'),
(1467, 12429, 'Ponyo', 'Welcome To A World Where Anything Is Possible.', 2008, 'The son of a sailor, 5-year old Sosuke lives a quiet life on an oceanside cliff with his mother Lisa. One fateful day, he finds a beautiful goldfish trapped in a bottle on the beach and upon rescuing her, names her Ponyo. But she is no ordinary goldfish. The daughter of a masterful wizard and a sea goddess, Ponyo uses her father''s magic to transform herself into a young girl and quickly falls in love with Sosuke, but the use of such powerful sorcery causes a dangerous imbalance in the world. As the moon steadily draws nearer to the earth and Ponyo''s father sends the ocean''s mighty waves to find his daughter, the two children embark on an adventure of a lifetime to save the world and fulfill Ponyo''s dreams of becoming human.', 7.5, 39.58676, 'ja', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/yp8vEZflGynlEylxEesbYasc06i.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h6XP82TyFWw'),
(1468, 228205, 'The Longest Ride', 'Two couples. Two love stories. One epic tale.', 2015, 'The lives of a young couple intertwine with a much older man as he reflects back on a lost love while he''s trapped in an automobile crash.', 7.3, 41.94652, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qdUVfvPBvT6cetDDM7rn8y2CNZE.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uEDb35R7na8'),
(1469, 2900, 'The Astronaut''s Wife', 'How well do you know the one you love?', 1999, 'When astronaut Spencer Armacost returns to Earth after a mission that nearly cost him his life, he decides to take a desk job in order to see his beautiful wife, Jillian, more often. Gradually, Jillian notices that Spencer''s personality seems to have changed, but her concerns fade when she discovers that she''s pregnant. As Jillian grows closer to becoming a mother, her suspicions about Spencer return. Why does it seem as if he''s a different person?', 5.4, 20.697556, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/54RGJ6INW9ERG8IaalmMKbbDgwH.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pu_TmXgGEG8'),
(1470, 21311, 'I Dreamed of Africa', 'Sometimes the adventure of a lifetime becomes life itself.', 2000, 'Inspired by the true story of indomitable Kuki Gallmann, the film tells of a beautiful and inquisitive woman who had the courage to escape from her comfortable yet monotonous life in Italy to start anew in the African wilderness with her son, Emanuele, and her new husband, Paolo. Gallmann faces great danger there but eventually becomes a celebrated conservationist.', 5.3, 1.656695, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kuDIrcsUI0duLSTUgKKLKEiEdrK.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gnya5boyEv8'),
(1471, 77875, 'Playing for Keeps', '', 2012, 'A former sports star who''s fallen on hard times starts coaching his son''s soccer team in an attempt to get his life together.', 5.4, 17.932562, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jYv6MqOoAIpxZd6ydJ4S5S2QHDZ.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=musnXxhyxik'),
(1472, 192136, 'Mandela: Long Walk to Freedom', 'It is an ideal for which I am prepared to die.', 2013, 'A chronicle of Nelson Mandela''s life journey from his childhood in a rural village through to his inauguration as the first democratically elected president of South Africa.', 6.5, 15.50957, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/nzjwDSwLbalv7bCXnFbkAuIxXLx.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0a8DQcS26Vs'),
(1473, 18254, 'Reds', 'Not since Gone With The Wind has there been a great romantic epic like it!', 1981, 'A radical American journalist becomes involved with the Communist revolution in Russia and hopes to bring its spirit and idealism to the United States.', 7.1, 4.602185, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3jOs4aWI7XSVIEaF8KMojNre7A7.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MLAnTuCs6_g'),
(1474, 881, 'A Few Good Men', '', 1992, 'When cocky military lawyer Lt. Daniel Kaffee and his co-counsel, Lt. Cmdr. JoAnne Galloway, are assigned to a murder case, they uncover a hazing ritual that could implicate high-ranking officials such as shady Col. Nathan Jessep.', 7.1, 40.379967, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rLOk4z9zL1tTukIYV56P94aZXKk.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uTE592ryZx4'),
(1475, 10877, 'Exit Wounds', 'This Is Gonna Hurt', 2001, 'Maverick cop Orin Boyd always brings down the domestic terrorists he tracks, but he ruffles feathers with his unorthodox techniques -- and soon finds himself reassigned to the toughest district in Detroit. When he discovers a group of detectives secretly operating a drug ring, Boyd joins forces with an unlikely ally -- gangster Latrell Walker -- to bring down the rotten cops.', 5.3, 12.601306, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tGIJhBejmredgUZRNdteZyiahag.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fx6Rbj5tbgE'),
(1476, 9600, 'Big Momma''s House', 'This FBI agent is going undercover... and he''s concealing more than a weapon.', 2000, 'When a street-smart FBI agent is sent to Georgia to protect a beautiful single mother and her son from an escaped convict, he is forced to impersonate a crass Southern granny known as Big Momma in order to remain incognito.', 5.6, 24.389194, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5YoSFqpTz5qIxsX61CPMGKONQIY.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=njhwlzuPXv4'),
(1477, 202575, 'Thunder and the House of Magic', 'One lost little cat. One magical adventure.', 2013, 'Thunder, an abandoned young cat seeking shelter from a storm, stumbles into the strangest house imaginable, owned by an old magician and inhabited by a dazzling array of automatons and gizmos. Not everyone welcomes the new addition to the troupe as Jack Rabbit and Maggie Mouse plot to evict Thunder. The situation gets worse when the magician lands in hospital and his scheming nephew sees his chance to cash in by selling the mansion. Our young hero is determined to earn his place and so he enlists the help of some wacky magician''s assistants to protect his magical new home.', 6.3, 12.867326, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3R13g2XgblynIrQGF8geFZJPNvR.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z6VKG3lZEIg'),
(1478, 71469, 'The Darkest Hour', 'Survive The Holidays', 2011, 'In Moscow, five young people lead the charge against an alien race which has attacked Earth via our power supply.', 4.8, 23.328823, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5Ao4qAFbjP7fcFOOdMNvQEnl0Yr.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IgXzLMQuQ6Y'),
(1479, 85446, 'Step Up Revolution', 'One Step Can Change Your World', 2012, 'Emily arrives in Miami with aspirations to become a professional dancer. She sparks with Sean, the leader of a dance crew whose neighborhood is threatened by Emily''s father''s development plans.', 6.7, 29.77544, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jMpwxmk3r7Aq36GcqMbCuP9DJYQ.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aEAt9eTi72w'),
(1480, 326, 'Snakes on a Plane', 'At 30,000 feet, snakes aren''t the deadliest thing on this plane.', 2006, 'America is on the search for the murderer Eddie Kim. Sean Jones must fly to L.A. to testify in a hearing against Kim. Accompanied by FBI agent Neville Flynn, the flight receives some unexpected visitors.', 5.1, 19.642328, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9wqWQ5rXQG6daMpowqwadGjI768.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WXkcJ5G04nI'),
(1481, 10685, 'The Watcher', 'Don''t go home alone.', 2000, 'FBI agent Joel Campbell, burnt-out and shell-shocked after years spent chasing serial killers, flees L.A. to begin a new life for himself in Chicago. But five months later, Joel''s best laid plans are abruptly cut short when his new hometown becomes the setting for some particularly gruesome murders--murders that could only have been committed by one man: David Allen Griffin. One of Joel''s most elusive and cunning nemeses, Griffin has followed his former pursuer to Chicago in order to play a sadistic game of cat and mouse. Taunting Joel with photographs of his intended victims and leaving his crime scenes meticulously free of clues in order to keep the police at bay, Griffin derives as much pleasure out of watching Joel react to every movement as watching his victims die. But when Griffin moves into Joel''s inner circle, Joel must quickly find some way to stop him before someone close to him becomes the next one to die.', 4.9, 7.339908, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hsMvndtd3KPAvJ3q7zKZuNSB1R3.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4P6gwL3sV2U'),
(1482, 7220, 'The Punisher', 'There is no justice, there is only revenge.', 2004, 'When undercover FBI agent Frank Castle''s wife and son are slaughtered, he becomes ''the Punisher'' -- a ruthless vigilante willing to go to any length to avenge his family.', 6.1, 35.09961, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7rmA1HwYp2GKM85BL0cVwCaosGr.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TqVSFchQEyM'),
(1483, 9763, 'Goal!: The Dream Begins', 'Every Dream Has A Beginning', 2005, 'Like millions of kids around the world, Santiago harbors the dream of being a professional footballer...However, living in the Barrios section of Los Angeles, he thinks it is only that--a dream. Until one day an extraordinary turn of events has him trying out for Premiership club Newcastle United.', 6.6, 16.541792, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9YZhJGoIbJtrjDYbENGhR6f6SZE.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=--qOSiMyD84'),
(1484, 72387, 'Safe', 'She has the code. He is the key.', 2012, 'After a former elite agent rescues a 12-year-old Chinese girl who''s been abducted, they find themselves in the middle of a standoff between Triads, the Russian Mafia and high-level corrupt New York City politicians and police.', 6.3, 31.92695, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kOCpkoMUVae9UIf85gO71SyjLbW.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=s3kTkk4k_5Q'),
(1485, 12596, 'Pushing Tin', 'A comedy about losing control', 1999, 'Two air traffic controllers (John Cusack, Billy Bob Thornton) who thrive on living dangerously compete to outdo each other on several levels.', 5.7, 9.060642, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/61FWajJNKeS27DO4KgvS5LUgcHh.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A2S6ys_XZCU'),
(1486, 1892, 'Return of the Jedi', 'The Empire Falls...', 1983, 'As Rebel leaders map their strategy for an all-out attack on the Emperor''s newer, bigger Death Star. Han Solo remains frozen in the cavernous desert fortress of Jabba the Hutt, the most loathsome outlaw in the universe, who is also keeping Princess Leia as a slave girl. Now a master of the Force, Luke Skywalker rescues his friends, but he cannot become a true Jedi Knight until he wages his own crucial battle against Darth Vader, who has sworn to win Luke over to the dark side of the Force.', 7.9, 46.50907, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jQYlydvHm3kUix1f8prMucrplhm.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NJZ83r9DlGc'),
(1487, 13460, 'Doomsday', 'Mankind has an expiration date.', 2008, 'A lethal virus spreads throughout the British isles,infecting millions and killing hundreds of thousands. To contain the threat, acting authorities brutally quarantine the country as it succumbs to fear and chaos. The quarantine is successful. Three decades later, the Reaper virus violently resurfaces in a major city. An elite group of specialists is urgently dispatched into the still-quarantined country to retrieve a cure by any means necessary. Shut off from the rest of the world, the unit must battle through a landscape that has become a waking nightmare.', 5.8, 21.538221, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cKUmTyXgmhv8cMRCY9RYTKcAeTn.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fJDVi0BMabU'),
(1488, 8055, 'The Reader', 'Behind the mystery lies a truth that will make you question everything you know.', 2008, 'The story of Michael Berg, a German lawyer who, as a teenager in the late 1950s, had an affair with an older woman, Hanna, who then disappeared only to resurface years later as one of the defendants in a war crimes trial stemming from her actions as a concentration camp guard late in the war. He alone realizes that Hanna is illiterate and may be concealing that fact at the expense of her freedom.', 7.2, 33.923786, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/r0WURbmnhgKeBpHcpDULBgRedQM.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JA1J2WmFGUw'),
(1489, 50647, 'Wanderlust', 'Leave your baggage behind', 2012, 'Rattled by sudden unemployment, a Manhattan couple surveys alternative living options, ultimately deciding to experiment with living on a rural commune where free love rules.', 5.3, 20.908495, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hH1Bla0W4YIn9sdd9NwODzDCcE4.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Oz7xMY1AbbI'),
(1490, 10719, 'Elf', 'This holiday, discover your inner elf.', 2003, 'When young Buddy falls into Santa''s gift sack on Christmas Eve, he''s transported back to the North Pole and raised as a toy-making elf by Santa''s helpers. But as he grows into adulthood, he can''t shake the nagging feeling that he doesn''t belong. Buddy vows to visit Manhattan and find his real dad, a workaholic publisher.', 6.4, 16.901955, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/oOleziEempUPu96jkGs0Pj6tKxj.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=14o38xfHlXc'),
(1491, 9294, 'Phenomenon', 'Some things in life just can''t be explained.', 1996, 'An ordinary man sees a bright light descend from the sky, and discovers he now has super-intelligence and telekinesis.', 6.2, 15.039407, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/roUYK9EXmgyDO48Qje7rZI4Qgav.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=apduYg2VqTI'),
(1492, 11888, 'Snow Dogs', 'Get ready for mush hour!', 2002, 'When a Miami dentist inherits a team of sled dogs, he''s got to learn the trade or lose his pack to a crusty mountain man.', 5.3, 13.655735, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8DDC6z1XyLSiNLzKw1pXcYeAOJ3.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g8OgyRrNL1A'),
(1493, 9647, 'Scrooged', 'The spirits will move you in odd and hysterical ways.', 1988, 'In this modern take on Charles Dickens'' "A Christmas Carol," Frank Cross (Bill Murray) is a wildly successful television executive whose cold ambition and curmudgeonly nature has driven away the love of his life, Claire Phillips (Karen Allen). But after firing a staff member, Eliot Loudermilk (Bobcat Goldthwait), on Christmas Eve, Frank is visited by a series of ghosts who give him a chance to re-evaluate his actions and right the wrongs of his past.', 6.7, 21.620317, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uO0znfB2ZzTXA1IS7jkrjNbpkYK.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3YjrsSEEreY'),
(1494, 9353, 'Nacho Libre', 'He''s not lean. He''s not mean. He''s nacho average hero.', 2006, 'Nacho Libre is loosely based on the story of Fray Tormenta ("Friar Storm"), aka Rev. Sergio Gutierrez Benitez, a real-life Mexican Catholic priest who had a 23-year career as a masked luchador. He competed in order to support the orphanage he directed. The producers are Jack Black, David Klawans, Julia Pistor, and Mike White.', 5.6, 14.642055, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kh7B91bMl2lZ0mH9WhPfaNUIEQH.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LCa1c0H9f1Q'),
(1495, 55721, 'Bridesmaids', 'Save the date', 2011, 'Annie’s life is a mess. But when she finds out her lifetime best friend is engaged, she simply must serve as Lillian’s maid of honor. Though lovelorn and broke, Annie bluffs her way through the expensive and bizarre rituals. With one chance to get it perfect, she’ll show Lillian and her bridesmaids just how far you’ll go for someone you love.', 6.5, 17.107065, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gJtA7hYsBMQ7EM3sPBMUdBfU7a0.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2p-S-cc6jzA'),
(1496, 109414, 'This Is the End', 'Nothing ruins a party like the end of the world.', 2013, 'While attending a party at James Franco''s house, Seth Rogen, Jay Baruchel and many other celebrities are faced with the apocalypse.', 6.3, 38.21708, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7Wdc3etyBJA4432TYtz6n9GQd1c.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kliQSsD_npo'),
(1497, 10307, 'Stigmata', 'The messenger must be silenced.', 1999, 'A young woman with no strong religious beliefs, Frankie Paige begins having strange and violent experiences, showing signs of the wounds that Jesus received when crucified. When the Vatican gets word of Frankie''s situation, a high-ranking cardinal requests that the Rev. Andrew Kiernan investigate her case. Soon Kiernan realizes that very sinister forces are at work, and tries to rescue Frankie from the entity that is plaguing her.', 6, 14.993169, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/p3Ead51dWRTXT9c0OHTes7tHZBP.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WzObOLaz6ng'),
(1498, 11978, 'Men of Honor', 'History is made by those who break the rules.', 2000, 'Against formidable odds -- and an old-school diving instructor embittered by the U.S. Navy''s new, less prejudicial policies -- Carl Brashear sets his sights on becoming the Navy''s first African-American master diver in this uplifting true story. Their relationship starts out on the rocks, but fate ultimately conspires to bring the men together into a setting of mutual respect, triumph and honor.', 7, 24.147268, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wNUAnXV1mzOOfvnVBIYsalkk078.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iC3pHZwdmGg'),
(1499, 22907, 'Takers', 'Who''s Taking Who?', 2010, 'A seasoned team of bank robbers, including Gordon Jennings (Idris Elba), John Rahway (Paul Walker), A.J. (Hayden Christensen), and brothers Jake (Michael Ealy) and Jesse Attica (Chris Brown) successfully complete their latest heist and lead a life of luxury while planning their next job. When Ghost (Tip T.I. Harris), a former member of their team, is released from prison he convinces the group to strike an armored car carrying $20 million. As the "Takers" carefully plot out their strategy and draw nearer to exacting the grand heist, a reckless police officer (Matt Dillon) inches closer to apprehending the criminals.', 6, 18.47242, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/s2zx7JA87rkQcmsV40k0vbVJ6oh.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0DItbZIVKhk');
