(2520, 16769, 'Coal Miner''s Daughter', 'She was married at 13. She had four kids by the time she was 20. She''s been hungry and poor. She''s been loved and cheated on. She became a singer because it was the only thing she could do. She became a star because it was the only way she could do it.', 1980, 'Biography of Loretta Lynn, a country and western singer that came from poverty to fame.', 7.2, 3.826685, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gx3qD1YVwNCuHR1jX7rPB6L6uxQ.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Pivm4oMEDRs'),
(2521, 33217, 'Diary of a Wimpy Kid', 'It''s not a diary, it''s a movie.', 2010, 'Greg Heffley is headed for big things, but first he has to survive the scariest, most humiliating experience of any kid’s life – middle school! That won’t be easy, considering he’s surrounded by hairy-freckled morons, wedgie-loving bullies and a moldy slice of cheese with nuclear cooties!', 5.9, 21.09549, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/iLAGiPnSuODt9cn332bkFElrRig.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=It4DJi918z4'),
(2522, 132232, 'Mama', 'A Mother''s Love is Forever', 2013, 'Guillermo del Toro presents Mama, a supernatural thriller that tells the haunting tale of two little girls who disappeared into the woods the day that their parents were killed. When they are rescued years later and begin a new life, they find that someone or something still wants to come tuck them in at night.', 6, 47.455147, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/eo8BhR8Q5STmWE9sMLsEPagxmy6.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I7_CLVoGkgA'),
