(2757, 14577, 'Dirty Work', 'Revenge is a dish best served DIRTY.', 1998, 'Unemployed and recently dumped, Mitch and his buddy Sam start a revenge-for-hire business to raise the $50,000 that Sam''s father needs to get a heart transplant. The dirty duo brings down a movie theater manager and hires hookers to pose as dead bodies during a live TV ad. When a wealthy developer hires the guys to trash a building (so that he can have it condemned), problems arise and a feud ensues.', 6.5, 9.066881, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/r6OcS6TQCHal2wHooJhHWSlFzfd.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fU81TsgFKqI'),
