(2794, 14574, 'The Boy in the Striped Pyjamas', 'Lines may divide us, but hope will unite us.', 2008, 'When his family moves from their home in Berlin to a strange new house in Poland, young Bruno befriends Shmuel, a boy who lives on the other side of the fence where everyone seems to be wearing striped pajamas. Unaware of Shmuel''s fate as a Jewish prisoner or the role his own Nazi father plays in his imprisonment, Bruno embarks on a dangerous journey inside the camp''s walls.', 7.7, 34.821224, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sLwYSEVVV3r047cjrpRAbGgNsfL.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uwysOfnX2Qg'),
(2795, 16, 'Dancer in the Dark', 'You don''t need eyes to see.', 2000, 'Selma, a Czech immigrant on the verge of blindness, struggles to make ends meet for herself and her son, who has inherited the same genetic disorder and will suffer the same fate without an expensive operation. When life gets too difficult, Selma learns to cope through her love of musicals, escaping life''s troubles - even if just for a moment - by dreaming up little numbers to the rhythmic beats of her surroundings.', 7.6, 22.022228, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9rsivF4sWfmBzrNr4LPu6TNJhXX.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ddcCwLqtT8w'),
(2796, 39780, 'Oscar and Lucinda', 'They dared to play the game of love, faith, and chance.', 1997, 'After a childhood of abuse by his evangelistic father, misfit Oscar Hopkins becomes an Anglican minister and develops a divine obsession with gambling. Lucinda Leplastrier is a rich Australian heiress shopping in London for materials for her newly acquired glass factory back home. Deciding to travel to Australia as a missionary, Oscar meets Lucinda aboard ship, and a mutual obsession blossoms. They make a wager that will alter each of their destinies.', 6.2, 0.139384, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9naDX3u4hsRM8jZ0Y7k5e2HAKmY.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q9KRbrmc-A0'),
