(2827, 13812, 'Quarantine', 'Contain The Truth.', 2008, 'A television reporter and her cameraman are trapped inside a building quarantined by the CDC after the outbreak of a mysterious virus which turns humans into bloodthirsty killers.', 5.5, 8.083995, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rGfOD8IC1x4PqmnqRuA8KyCckia.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ydUV2w59Ydg'),
