(2976, 316727, 'The Purge: Election Year', 'Keep America great', 2016, 'Two years after choosing not to kill the man who killed his son, former police sergeant Leo Barnes has become head of security for Senator Charlene Roan, the front runner in the next Presidential election due to her vow to eliminate the Purge. On the night of what should be the final Purge, a betrayal from within the government forces Barnes and Roan out onto the street where they must fight to survive the night.', 6.1, 53.727146, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gg7tlp45xqGWMra0sqQVPvybje2.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9rqIJcY9hMc'),
(2977, 10314, 'She''s All That', 'These two opposites attract... but EVERYONE''S trying to keep them apart!', 1999, 'High school hotshot Zach Siler is the envy of his peers. But his popularity declines sharply when his cheerleader girlfriend, Taylor, leaves him for sleazy reality-television star Brock Hudson. Desperate to revive his fading reputation, Siler agrees to a seemingly impossible challenge. He has six weeks to gain the trust of nerdy outcast Laney Boggs -- and help her to become the school''s next prom queen.', 5.7, 8.9876, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/a0pepZNFCjggc7Na9gEwbTI1f46.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kI9fYsgduGE'),
(2978, 663, 'Saw IV', 'You think it is over...but the games have just begun', 2007, 'Jigsaw and his apprentice Amanda are dead. Now, upon the news of Detective Kerry''s murder, two seasoned FBI profilers, Agent Strahm and Agent Perez, arrive in the terrified community to assist the veteran Detective Hoffman in sifting through Jigsaw''s latest grisly remains and piecing together the puzzle. However, when SWAT Commander Rigg is abducted and thrust into a game, the last officer untouched by Jigsaw has but ninety minutes to overcome a series of demented traps and save an old friend...or face the deadly consequences.', 5.9, 29.244768, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wd6mhwDjlpeOufuMUF1FAeMliWZ.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OxwdZMMymqY'),
(2979, 11804, 'White Noise', 'The line separating the living from the dead has been crossed.', 2005, 'An architect''s desire to speak with his wife from beyond the grave using EVP (Electronic Voice Phenomenon), becomes an obsession with supernatural repercussions.', 5.6, 14.447723, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ncB9SvOclmXYALlcAsF1jRIuISl.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=haHHr5_VX7I'),
(2980, 16781, 'Madea''s Family Reunion', '', 2006, 'Based upon Tyler Perry''s acclaimed stage production, Madea''s Family Reunion continues the adventures of Southern matriarch Madea. She has just been court ordered to be in charge of Nikki, a rebellious runaway, her nieces, Lisa and Vanessa, are suffering relationship trouble, and through it all, she has to organize her family reunion.', 6, 5.882208, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kDCCXEm902lfZB51sf6MWCpYqIb.jpg', NULL),
(2981, 11873, 'The Color of Money', 'The Hustler isn''t what he used to be. But he has the next best thing. A kid who is.', 1986, 'Former pool hustler "Fast Eddie" Felson decides he wants to return to the game by taking a pupil. He meets talented but green Vincent Lauria and proposes a partnership. As they tour pool halls, Eddie teaches Vincent the tricks of scamming, but he eventually grows frustrated with Vincent''s showboat antics, leading to an argument and a falling-out. Eddie takes up playing again and soon crosses paths with Vincent as an opponent.', 6.7, 17.3393, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dVdnHmdQu3JtLAAksjTmTEF76gD.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HgLvznCiNUo'),
(2982, 9289, 'The Longest Day', 'This is the day that changed the world... When history held its breath.', 1962, 'The retelling of June 6, 1944, from the perspectives of the Germans, US, British, Canadians, and the Free French. Marshall Erwin Rommel, touring the defenses being established as part of the Reich''s Atlantic Wall, notes to his officers that when the Allied invasion comes they must be stopped on the beach. "For the Allies as well as the Germans, it will be the longest day"', 7.2, 19.524973, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5zmvEofdIlgXrQl9A7e5IOzlnFU.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nqFn_pM5QxU'),
(2983, 10414, 'The Mighty Ducks', 'They can''t skate. They can''t win. They can''t be serious.', 1992, 'After reckless young lawyer Gordon Bombay gets arrested for drunk driving, he must coach a kids hockey team for his community service. Gordon has experience on the ice, but isn''t eager to return to hockey, a point hit home by his tense dealings with his own former coach, Jack Reilly. The reluctant Gordon eventually grows to appreciate his team, which includes promising young Charlie Conway, and leads them to take on Reilly''s tough players.', 6.4, 8.932837, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zxaCHxKDFNi6frh1Q0dj19L216o.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Um_JU7HpSYQ'),
(2984, 1970, 'The Grudge', 'It never forgives. It never forgets.', 2004, 'American nurse, Karen Davis moves to Tokyo and encounters a vengeful supernatural spirit known as The Grudge that often possesses its victims. When a series of horrifying and mysterious deaths occur – with the spirit passing its curse onto each victim - Karen must find away to break the spell before she becomes the spirit''s next victim.', 5.8, 35.695442, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5AGB8FVELnhMMw3nO372sw1xp58.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tqn2t3PefdY'),
(2985, 9614, 'Happy Gilmore', 'He doesn''t play golf... he destroys it.', 1996, 'Failed hockey player-turned-golf whiz Happy Gilmore -- whose unconventional approach and antics on the grass courts the ire of rival Shooter McGavin -- is determined to win a PGA tournament so he can save his granny''s house with the prize money. Meanwhile, an attractive tour publicist tries to soften Happy''s image.', 6.5, 26.598885, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4RnCeRzvI1xk5tuNWjpDKzSnJDk.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y1emDAYCfVQ'),
(2986, 8922, 'Jeepers Creepers', 'What’s eating you?', 2001, 'A college-age brother and sister get more than they bargained for on their road trip home from spring break. When the bickering siblings witness a creepy truck driver tossing body bags into a sewer near an abandoned church, they investigate. Bad move! Opening a Pandora''s Box of unspeakable evil, the pair must flee for their lives -- with a monstrous "shape" in hot pursuit.', 6.1, 23.316208, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/g410Y1U1ELbmJG14Zru3UAimm1G.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ACMqG1WdPQk'),
(2987, 1648, 'Bill & Ted''s Excellent Adventure', 'History is about to be rewritten by two guys who can''t spell.', 1989, 'In the small town of San Dimas, a few miles away from Los Angeles, there are two nearly brain dead teenage boys going by the names of Bill S, Preston ESQ. and Ted Theodore Logan, they have a dream together of starting their own rock and roll band called the "Wyld Stallyns". Unfortunately, they are still in high school and on the verge of failing out of their school as well, and if they do not pass their upcoming history report, they will be separated as a result of Ted''s father sending him to military school. But, what Bill and Ted do not know is that they must stay together to save the future. So, a man from the future named Rufus came to help them pass their report. So, both Bill and Ted decided to gather up historical figures which they need for their report. They are hoping that this will help them pass their report so they can stay together.', 6.7, 25.929893, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tV25lGWGWGEqUe3U0xjQTBgilSx.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gxFxklxvE_w'),
(2988, 17917, 'Oliver!', 'Much Much More Than a Musical!', 1968, 'Musical adaptation of Charles Dickens'' Oliver Twist, a classic tale of an orphan who runs away from the workhouse and joins up with a group of boys headed by the Artful Dodger and trained to be pickpockets by master thief Fagin.', 7, 8.305998, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1XJgoaOWKrqxkKeBKWLKSigqG8c.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PKKLLm715iw'),
(2989, 74534, 'The Best Exotic Marigold Hotel', 'Share the journey. Share the laughter.', 2011, 'British retirees travel to India to take up residence in what they believe is a newly restored hotel. Less luxurious than its advertisements, the Marigold Hotel nevertheless slowly begins to charm in unexpected ways as the residents find new purpose in their old age.', 6.9, 21.258991, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gNWiOKTWDvPTpr7QfPWk18gLftz.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UbJssTq5oNs'),
(2990, 19405, 'Recess: School''s Out', 'Saving The World One Playground At A Time', 2001, 'Recess: School''s Out is a 2001 animated film based on the Disney television series Recess. This film was produced by Walt Disney Pictures and was released theatrically nationwide on February 16, 2001.It''s the most exciting time of year at Third Street Elementary-- the end of the School Year! But boredom quickly sets in for protagonist TJ Detweiler, as his friends are headed for Summer Camp. One day, while passing by the school on his bike, he notices a green glow coming from the school''s auditorium. This is the work of the insidious ex-principal of Third Street, Phillium Benedict and his gang of ninjas and secret service look-alikes! Benedict is planning to get rid of Summer Vacation using his newly-acquired Tractor Beam, which he stole from the US Military Base in an effort to raise US Test Scores, and it''s up to the Recess Gang to stop him! In the end.', 6.6, 5.699058, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/yLdsXdgB2VJ2uBQvYaEB5xPELlq.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9cRn-bV5vdc'),
(2991, 9355, 'Mad Max Beyond Thunderdome', 'Two men enter. One man leaves.', 1985, 'Mad Max becomes a pawn in a decadent oasis of a technological society, and when exiled, becomes the deliverer of a colony of children.', 5.9, 36.58204, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jJlxcEVVUHnrUeEkQ0077VeHQpb.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vynTmqiizog'),
(2992, 10999, 'Commando', 'Somewhere... somehow... someone''s going to pay.', 1985, 'John Matrix, the former leader of a special commando strike force that always got the toughest jobs done, is forced back into action when his young daughter is kidnapped. To find her, Matrix has to fight his way through an array of punks, killers, one of his former commandos, and a fully equipped private army. With the help of a feisty stewardess and an old friend, Matrix has only a few hours to overcome his greatest challenge: finding his daughter before she''s killed.', 6.4, 34.224205, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ollPAAAgZ7euU8VisfqU3cuXhZ6.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VgDU6sOu334'),
(2993, 321258, 'The Boy', 'Every child needs to feel loved.', 2016, 'A nanny, working for a family whose son has just passed away, finds herself put in charge of caring for a lifelike doll that the couple treat as a real child.', 5.8, 38.17948, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kW2vgzhyWXQu5UxNzebPokipBqH.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jfhHg3eeqS0'),
(2994, 44040, 'Devil', 'Bad Things Happen For A Reason', 2010, 'A group of people trapped in a elevator realizes that the devil is among them.', 5.8, 30.934689, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/aivXPSi53H95BoUa5njEYso389s.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wYy7igKD21A');
INSERT INTO "public"."movies" ("id", "tmdb_id", "title", "tagline", "release_year", "overview", "score", "popularity", "language", "poster_url", "trailer_url") VALUES
(2995, 10426, 'Friday After Next', 'The party''s back in the ''hood!', 2002, 'Craig and Day Day have finally moved out of their parents houses and into their own crib. The cousins work nights at a local mall as security guards. When their house is robbed on Christmas Eve they team up to track him down.', 6, 7.499639, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sxHFGPKLWj9e3aaA6wGVxghoiPE.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H3g5QQynaJk'),
(2996, 280092, 'Insidious: Chapter 3', 'This is how you die', 2015, 'A twisted new tale of terror begins for a teenage girl and her family, predating the haunting of the Lambert family in the earlier movies and revealing more mysteries of the otherworldly realm The Further.', 6.2, 45.946526, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/iDdGfdNvY1EX0uDdA4Ru77fwMfc.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eiDph99MdZ4'),
(2997, 13938, 'The Last Dragon', 'His family thinks he''s crazy. His enemies think he''s no challenge. But she knows he''s THE LAST DRAGON.', 1985, 'A young man searches for the "master" to obtain the final level of martial arts mastery known as the glow. Along the way he must fight an evil martial arts expert and rescue a beautiful singer from an obsessed music promoter.', 6.4, 4.928777, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/r5QnLY30gXlZ8luiJE3quDs1WNF.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=10qwLUnm4qE'),
(2998, 10163, 'The Lawnmower Man', 'God made him simple. Science made him a god.', 1992, 'A simple man is turned into a genius through the application of computer science.', 5.4, 10.125029, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1VLqWcel87oYVmN383FgSH0mCTY.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zzwPuJklv4w'),
(2999, 12182, 'Nick and Norah''s Infinite Playlist', 'Every night has a soundtrack.', 2008, 'Nick cannot stop obsessing over his ex-girlfriend, Tris, until Tris'' friend Norah suddenly shows interest in him at a club. Thus beings an odd night filled with ups and downs as the two keep running into Tris and her new boyfriend while searching for Norah''s drunken friend, Caroline, with help from Nick''s band mates. As the night winds down, the two have to figure out what they want from each other.', 6.4, 20.45245, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cndxWgZEHnSUtytrMjal97ye34E.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0yYcfsYZaWU'),
(3000, 1832, 'Dogma', 'It can be Hell getting into Heaven', 1999, 'The latest battle in the eternal war between Good and Evil has come to New Jersey in the late, late 20th Century. Angels, demons, apostles and prophets (of a sort) walk among the cynics and innocents of America and duke it out for the fate of humankind.', 6.8, 14.543435, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xI5beD8Td79E2uZNAxgd1gWWOEd.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j4rIdRC2DMA');
INSERT INTO "public"."movies" ("id", "tmdb_id", "title", "tagline", "release_year", "overview", "score", "popularity", "language", "poster_url", "trailer_url") VALUES
(3001, 9034, 'The Banger Sisters', 'Some friendships last forever... like it or not.', 2002, 'In the late ''60s, the self-proclaimed belles of the rock ''n'' roll ball, rocked the worlds of every music legend whose pants they could take off -- and they have the pictures to prove it. But it''s been more than two decades since the Banger Sisters earned their nickname -- or even laid eyes on each other. Their reunion is the collision of two women''s worlds; one who''s living in the past, and one who''s hiding from it. Together they learn to live in the moment.', 5.5, 6.015354, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bfXXqz4yvsHnQwwOSa23ASUaGXA.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N_mVkZ426vs'),
(3002, 15301, 'Twilight Zone: The Movie', 'You''re travelling through another dimension. A dimension, not only of sight and sound, but of mind. A journey into a wondrous land whose boundaries are that of imagination. Next stop, the Twilight Zone!', 1983, 'Four directors collaborated to remake four episodes of the popular television series ''The Twilight Zone'' for this movie. The episodes are updated slightly and in color (the television show was in black-and-white), but very true to the originals, where eerie and disturbing situations gradually spin out of control. "A Quality of Mercy", "Kick the Can", "It''s a Good Life", and "Nightmare at 20,000 Feet".', 6.2, 12.902975, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9dKBVzAQQ2Utht2DPdWA654QPFm.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Vcx-Kx_WOvQ'),
(3003, 10135, 'Road House', 'Dalton lives like a loner, fights like a professional. And loves like there''s no tomorrow.', 1989, 'The Double Deuce is the meanest, loudest and rowdiest bar south of the Mason-Dixon Line, and Dalton (Patrick Swayze) has been hired to clean it up. He might not look like much, but the Ph.D.-educated bouncer proves he''s more than capable -- busting the heads of troublemakers and turning the roadhouse into a jumping hot-spot. But Dalton''s romance with the gorgeous Dr. Clay (Kelly Lynch) puts him on the bad side of cutthroat local big shot Brad Wesley (Ben Gazzara).', 6.3, 6.216203, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/r2hGyhvNneAifk7UpwAYxrkeFO4.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ku-f67Mb92o'),
(3004, 26352, 'A Low Down Dirty Shame', 'He''s armed and dangerously funny.', 1994, 'A black detective becomes embroiled in a web of danger while searching for a fortune in missing drug money. During the course of his investigation, he encounters various old connections, ultimately confronting the criminal responsible for Shame''s expulsion from the force. He must also deal with two women, Angela, a beautiful old flame, and Peaches, his energetic but annoying sidekick.', 6, 3.290639, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/v5XUfLrdoGfatObGXhqckYTNqFT.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-kRfPEO_5aY'),
(3005, 20616, 'Swimfan', 'His biggest fan just became his worst nightmare.', 2002, 'Ben Cronin has it all: the admiration of his many friends, a terrific girlfriend, and he''s on the fast-track to an athletic scholarship. Ben''s rock-solid, promising future and romance are turned upside-down with the arrival of Madison Bell. Madison, the new girl in town, quickly sets her sights on the impressionable Ben. While their first few meetings are innocent enough, the obsessive and seductive Madison wants more ... much more.', 5, 4.844451, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sHSRRxzBeUtxMosSqpCcBiGnPYI.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W-RGVruG7Y0'),
(3006, 9794, 'Employee of the Month', 'A slacker competes with a repeat winner for the "Employee of the Month" title at work', 2006, 'When he hears that the new female employee digs ambitious men who are the store employee of the month, a slacker gets his act together but finds himself in competition with his rival, an ambitious co-worker.', 5.3, 9.559737, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vfALEF9wz4CEep071iOwM5Qqd17.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uq96WOiaL08'),
(3007, 15037, 'Can''t Hardly Wait', 'Yesterday''s history.  Tomorrow''s the future.  Tonight''s the party.', 1998, 'It''s graduation day at Huntington Hills High, and you know what that means - time to party. And not just any party, either. This one will be a night to remember, as the nerds become studs, the jocks are humiliated, and freshman crushes blossom into grown-up romance.', 6.1, 11.350382, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/r3a5gGWfS0SDS9nriNrJzSSrErf.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qukvN6ieeMY'),
(3008, 227, 'The Outsiders', 'They grew up on the outside of society. They weren''t looking for a fight. They were looking to belong.', 1983, 'When two poor greasers, Johnny, and Ponyboy are assaulted by a vicious gang, the socs, and Johnny kills one of the attackers, tension begins to mount between the two rival gangs, setting off a turbulent chain of events.', 6.9, 13.455373, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pl8Tf36TAOb2i561yPbQ9xl4P4D.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3ud6PLVjY5Y'),
(3009, 294272, 'Pete''s Dragon', 'Some secrets are too big to keep.', 2016, 'Pete is a mysterious 10-year-old with no family and no home who claims to live in the woods with a giant, green dragon named Elliott. With the help of Natalie, an 11-year-old girl whose father Jack owns the local lumber mill, forest ranger Grace sets out to determine where Pete came from, where he belongs, and the truth about this dragon.', 6.2, 31.97436, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/A9x4Ogk8KUXTfU649NS6lS9TCmu.jpg', NULL),
(3010, 11336, 'The Dead Zone', 'In his mind, he has the power to see the future. In his hands, he has the power to change it.', 1983, 'Johnny Smith is a schoolteacher with his whole life ahead of him but, after leaving his fiancee''s home one night, is involved in a car crash which leaves him in a coma for 5 years. When he wakes, he discovers he has an ability to see into the past, present and future life of anyone with whom he comes into physical contact.', 6.9, 16.78512, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9yTVaeS8eIkOpbwIycVFm7EQrgF.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qxJp_VQ5VUk'),
(3011, 283445, 'Sinister 2', 'Be careful, children at play.', 2015, 'A young mother and her twin sons move into a rural house that''s marked for death.', 5.4, 26.090494, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hF6ORyihtAWHqKkIQI8BSpLQyON.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=45zJGfEoUAg'),
(3012, 88036, 'Sparkle', 'Celebrate the legend.', 2012, 'Musical prodigy, Sparkle (Jordin Sparks) struggles to become a star while overcoming issues that are tearing her family apart. From an affluent Detroit area and daughter to a single mother (Whitney Houston), she tries to balance a new romance with music manager Stix (Derek Luke) while dealing with the unexpected challenges her new life will bring as she and her two sisters (Carmen Ejogo and Tika Sumpter) strive to become a dynamic singing group during the Motown-era.', 5.8, 2.698185, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6LqVIhz0xxoFjiGjftDW69DbvNi.jpg', NULL),
(3013, 10984, 'Valentine', 'Remember that kid everyone ignored on Valentine’s Day? - He remembers you.', 2001, 'Five friends are stalked and murdered by a masked assailant while preparing for Valentine''s Day.', 5, 5.904126, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jMtWV4FixMGTgUjbr9NFVEANGYQ.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9KYtyaXIXZQ'),
(3014, 22824, 'The Fourth Kind', 'There are four kinds of alien encounters. The fourth kind is abduction.', 2009, 'Since the 1960s, a disproportionate number of the population in and around Nome, Alaska, have gone missing. Despite FBI investigations, the disappearances remain a mystery. Dr. Abigail Tyler, a psychologist, may be on the verge of blowing the unsolved cases wide open when, during the course of treating her patients, she finds evidence of alien abductions.', 5.8, 22.888172, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vfnsGUwurUQqlpvArBvUVc9rYXa.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JQBU4HvN5MY'),
(3015, 9526, 'A Prairie Home Companion', 'Radio Like You''ve Never Seen It Before', 2006, 'A look at what goes on backstage during the last broadcast of America''s most celebrated radio show, where singing cowboys Dusty and Lefty, a country music siren, and a host of others hold court', 6.4, 5.025446, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7AxXWJYzrFx7LIFP3OvCPecwXGE.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DE3TZSdjVFM'),
(3016, 39349, 'Sugar Hill', 'He wanted power. He wanted revenge. Now he just wants out.', 1994, 'Sugar Hill is a 1994 American crime-drama/neo-noir film starring Wesley Snipes and Michael Wright as brothers Roemello and Raynathan Skuggs. The film focuses on the two brothers, who are major drug dealers in the Harlem neighborhood of New York City.', 5.2, 2.580808, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6bnYhhJS7vuDMRPVSplWaXdK49g.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D6oxEZ6yblA'),
(3017, 15983, 'Invasion U.S.A.', 'America wasn''t ready...but HE was!', 1985, 'A one-man army comes to the rescue of the United States when a spy attempts an invasion.', 5.3, 4.192064, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mE5dSRTKW1dzV7D0pgP8sMxyIa9.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-ttJX4Z1hzk'),
(3018, 14544, 'Roll Bounce', '', 2005, 'From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia. Roll Bounce is a 2005 American comedy-drama film written by Norman Vance Jr. and directed by Malcolm D. Lee. The film stars hip hop artist Bow Wow as the leader of a roller skating crew in 1970s Chicago. The film also stars Nick Cannon, Meagan Good, Brandon T. Jackson, Wesley Jonathan, Chi McBride, Kellita Smith, and Jurnee Smollett. Description above from the Wikipedia article Roll Bounce, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.', 6.1, 2.596338, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lStFr3EHTNbnyOdOk2QDCqYGnlR.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KRbtDCxcN-M'),
(3019, 11545, 'Rushmore', 'Love. Expulsion. Revolution.', 1998, 'When a beautiful first-grade teacher arrives at a prep school, she soon attracts the attention of an ambitious teenager named Max, who quickly falls in love with her. Max turns to the father of two of his schoolmates for advice on how to woo the teacher. However, the situation soon gets complicated when Max''s new friend becomes involved with her, setting the two pals against one another in a war for her attention.', 7.5, 18.289303, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hSJ6swahAuZ8wM96lHDTwQPXUvZ.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=846UzdeHI1g'),
(3020, 42684, 'Skyline', 'Don''t look up', 2010, 'When strange lights descend on the city of Los Angeles, people are drawn outside like moths to a flame where an extraterrestrial force threatens to swallow the entire human population off the face of the Earth. Now the band of survivors must fight for their lives as the world unravels around them.', 4.7, 26.26821, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ehythjMSfqrJSWeCSSTw4WQe6b5.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mnoW5-DmIUM'),
(3021, 268238, 'The Second Best Exotic Marigold Hotel', '', 2015, 'As the Best Exotic Marigold Hotel has only a single remaining vacancy - posing a rooming predicament for two fresh arrivals - Sonny pursues his expansionist dream of opening a second hotel.', 6.3, 17.592299, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/j4PARl3gDpv2K45YAv0tgocLW5K.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3REYWGRmLnQ'),
(3022, 8359, 'Kit Kittredge: An American Girl', 'Kit Kittredge, a resourceful young girl, helps her mother run a boardinghouse after her father loses his job.', 2008, 'The Great Depression hits home for nine year old Kit Kittredge when her dad loses his business and leaves to find work. Oscar nominee Abigail Breslin stars as Kit, leading a splendid cast in the first ever "American Girl" theatrical movie. In order to keep their home, Kit and her mother must take in boarders - paying house - guests who turn out to be full of fascinating stories. When mother''s lockbox containing all their money is stolen, Kit''s new hobo friend Will is the prime suspect. Kit refuses to believe that Will would steal, and her efforts to sniff out the real story get her and friends into big trouble. The police say the robbery was an inside job, committed by someone they know. So if it wasn''t Will, then who did it.', 6.4, 6.27141, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/niHi0hJSryO5DpSVNCMASc3EELc.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F_tl7YF2tFc'),
(3023, 15648, 'The Perfect Man', 'Is it all too good to be true?', 2005, 'Holly is tired of moving every time her mom Jean breaks up with yet another second-rate guy. To distract her mother from her latest bad choice, Holly conceives the perfect plan for the perfect man, an imaginary secret admirer who will romance Jean and boost her self-esteem.', 5.5, 11.158906, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/s1zaWMtjzw1hm5tPXm2GLFJaCfY.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uXhk2QJm-14'),
(3024, 41823, 'Mo'' Better Blues', '', 1990, 'Opens with Bleek as a child learning to play the trumpet, his friends want him to come out and play but mother insists he finish his lessons. Bleek grows into adulthood and forms his own band - The Bleek Gilliam Quartet. The story of Bleek''s and Shadow''s friendly rivalry on stage which spills into their professional relationship and threatens to tear apart the quartet.', 6.3, 3.079862, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/223W6PWAiYb3BX2rbFvzjbDDIvz.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=io8Jw9BRRFY'),
(3025, 11891, 'Kung Pow: Enter the Fist', '', 2002, 'A movie within a movie, created to spoof the martial arts genre. Writer/director Steve Oedekerk uses contemporary characters and splices them into a 1970s kung-fu film, weaving the new and old together.
INSERT INTO "public"."movies" ("id", "tmdb_id", "title", "tagline", "release_year", "overview", "score", "popularity", "language", "poster_url", "trailer_url") VALUES
(3494, 58882, 'Snow Flower and the Secret Fan', '', 2011, 'A story set in 19th century China and centered on the lifelong friendship between two girls who develop their own secret code as a way to contend with the rigid cultural norms imposed on women.', 5.3, 2.260315, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lhhlq19I9BjcfmGLZc7SzHQULo0.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Aa93drpm30E'),
(3495, 7547, 'Come Early Morning', 'Before you fall in love, you need to love yourself.', 2006, 'Lucy wakes up in bed with a stranger and obviously from a night of drinking. She checks out and pays for the motel room on her account. Through her grandmother, she finds out her father is in town and pays him a visit. She agrees to go to his new church.', 5.9, 3.427061, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/holWpjqKXz6FyBUFA3LZIylMXyI.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bGOOOwPQm5M'),
(3496, 35944, 'Lucky Break', '', 2001, 'Half-way through his 12-year prison sentence for an incompetent armed robbery, Jimmy Hands gets a lucky break: he''s transferred to a prison from which he can probably escape. He convinces the governor to stage a musical in an old chapel next to the prison''s outer wall. He rounds up volunteer actors and puts his escape plan into production. Two other barriers, besides the wall, confront him: the arrival of a nasty inmate, John Toombes, who insists on joining the escape, and Jimmy''s feelings of attraction for Anabel, a social worker who agrees to appear in the play. Opening night approaches: is this Jimmy''s breakout performance?', 6.5, 0.669169, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/63JHVXD2bkPBdIFgprqXKu3k8bw.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NStGkCjDOBY'),
(3497, 42222, 'Julia', 'The story of two women whose friendship suddenly became a matter of life and death.', 1977, 'At the behest of an old and dear friend, playwright Lillian Hellman undertakes a dangerous mission to smuggle funds into Nazi Germany.', 6.3, 6.077735, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qHtPzs9eVCilp88c1arq73gH6xk.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U_u7Hvj14s0'),
(3498, 13827, 'Surfer, Dude', '', 2008, 'A wave twisting tale of a soul searching surfer experiencing an existential crisis.', 4.7, 2.404626, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/948AdP72iLQUjWvKp9r8981PT28.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7ekfP43ZLa4'),
(3499, 44260, 'Lake of Fire', 'Exploring the Issue that Divides the World', 2006, 'An unflinching look at the how the battle over abortion rights has played out in the United States over the last 15 years', 8, 0.475748, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uFdUv0neGCpaYLRJN45mnpc0pdR.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-b6h0lsiQcw'),
(3500, 9282, '11:14', 'Fate can change in seconds.', 2003, 'Tells the seemingly random yet vitally connected story of a set of incidents that all converge one evening at 11:14pm. The story follows the chain of events of five different characters and five different storylines that all converge to tell the story of murder and deceit.', 6.8, 15.048067, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3TFB0Doe92l9Jgc5qtUnE6r9rqt.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XS8gh5qMlFw');
INSERT INTO "public"."movies" ("id", "tmdb_id", "title", "tagline", "release_year", "overview", "score", "popularity", "language", "poster_url", "trailer_url") VALUES
(3501, 38940, 'Men of War', 'Killers for hire are paid for what they can do, not for what they believe... until today.', 1994, 'Nick Gunar is a burnt-out, jaded and hard-up former mercenary who is having a difficult time adjusting to civilian life. At the end of his rope, he is hired by the Nitro Mine Corporation to strong-arm the natives of a South China Sea island into giving up their rights to its valuable mineral resources. Nick loathes the thought of another mission, but this seemingly easy job will earn him enough money to get back with his estranged family. He recruits some of his former mercenary buddies to help him with the job. The island people refuse to give up their land and Nick decides to help them fight the greedy corporation that hired him. As greed and treachery begin to unravel, Nick''s band of mercenaries choose sides.', 5.4, 1.734764, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rrwG9foUMulWBI2Nk7s6Bcgwfim.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wEU1Qz9pnGM'),
(3502, 35689, 'Don McKay', 'Some secrets are better left buried.', 2009, 'Everything appears off-kilter when a man returns to his hometown after 25 years to visit his former lover.', 5.4, 1.496454, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pkziSZ6vmwFnhybgBAM96Q6xKMr.jpg', NULL),
(3503, 97614, 'Deadfall', 'Twisty thriller... a wild ride.', 2012, 'A thriller that follows two siblings who decide to fend for themselves in the wake of a botched casino heist, and their unlikely reunion during another family''s Thanksgiving celebration.', 5.6, 10.19041, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5ZM6uKhuEzWZD3xklmqKPuvq1Nj.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UqjlM_J93Yk'),
(3504, 37206, 'A Shine of Rainbows', 'An abandoned child brings the colors of love into their lives.', 2009, 'An orphaned boy named Tomás is adopted by Maire O’Donnell to live on a whimsical Irish isle filled with new friends, secret caves and a lost baby pup seal stranded on the coast. But when Maire''s reluctant husband Alec refuses to accept Tomás as his own son, the boy drifts down a fateful path of adventure and self-discovery, illuminating how rainbows can shine around - and within - us all.', 6.3, 12.099486, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9FWxI20tzm9LuP3KT9cbmp5YN6Q.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T3UiG6AXKrc'),
(3505, 58626, 'The Hit List', 'Who''s on your list?', 2011, 'A disgruntled man creates a hit list with a stranger during a drunken night out and must then race to try to save those he marked for extermination as the bodies begin to pile up and all fingers point to him.', 5.2, 4.957014, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tR88diuLaMMdxl9rBVdAKERzIjo.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O3MsVkfYwJg'),
(3506, 183894, 'Emma', '', 2009, 'Emma Woodhouse seems to be perfectly content, a loving father whom she cares for, friends, and a home. But Emma has a terrible habit - matchmaking. She cannot resist finding suitors for her friends, most of all Harriet Smith. Emma is desperate for Harriet to find happiness, but every suitor she finds for her friend ends up attracted to Emma herself. But is Emma so focused on Harriet''s happiness that she is not considering her own happiness in love?', 7.6, 2.135689, 'en', NULL, NULL),
(3507, 837, 'Videodrome', 'First it controls your mind. Then it destroys your body.', 1983, 'A sleazy cable-TV programmer begins to see his life and the future of media spin out of control in a very unusual fashion when he acquires a new kind of programming for his station.', 7.1, 18.119265, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qqqkiZSU9EBGZ1KiDmfn07S7qvv.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v8BUXKcp8zE'),
(3508, 1555, 'The Spanish Apartment', 'They came from Paris, Rome, London and Berlin to... the Spanish Apartment... where a year can change a lifetime.', 2002, 'A strait-laced French student moves into an apartment in Barcelona with a cast of six other characters from all over Europe. Together, they speak the international language of love and friendship.', 7, 13.034602, 'fr', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/baDm4V3Dqx2hNh7WF1NvGrHGgqQ.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AsvJFtUDfl0'),
(3509, 244783, 'Song One', 'A moment can change everything.', 2014, 'Estranged from her family, Franny returns home when an accident leaves her brother comatose. Retracing his life as an aspiring musician, she tracks down his favorite musician, James Forester. Against the backdrop of Brooklyn’s music scene, Franny and James develop an unexpected relationship and face the realities of their lives.', 5.5, 6.349218, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/a6dSJIEMxZFvQ7XJy4sf9fR0p7f.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ihdJgH757A0'),
(3510, 16564, 'Winter in Wartime', 'In 1945 Holland, a boy must choose between good and evil.', 2008, 'During World War II in the freezing Netherlands winter of 1944/1945 the western Netherlands are in the grip of a famine.  Many people move east to provide for their families. Fourteen year old Michiel can''t wait to join the Dutch resistance, to the dismay of his father, who, as mayor, works to prevent escalations in the village.', 6.8, 5.013575, 'nl', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pTZY4fWGh4noXdPXEKOcnOycKp5.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YrtnYwQXr6Y'),
(3511, 168027, 'Freaky Deaky', 'Crime is such a trippy thing', 2012, 'Set in 1974, a pair of ''60s radicals rely on their bomb-making skills on their way to becoming capitalists.', 4.9, 4.448353, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1rMr42ppp05ikGgoJf1efx0ouJZ.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IwCL9wdiPyc'),
(3512, 3482, 'The Train', 'It carried their hopes, their nation''s honour!', 1964, 'As the Allied forces approach Paris in August 1944, German Colonel Von Waldheim is desperate to take all of France''s greatest paintings to Germany. He manages to secure a train to transport the valuable art works even as the chaos of retreat descends upon them. The French resistance however wants to stop them from stealing their national treasures but have received orders from London that they are not to be destroyed. The station master, Labiche, is tasked with scheduling the train and making it all happen smoothly but he is also part of a dwindling group of resistance fighters tasked with preventing the theft. He and others stage an elaborate ruse to keep the train from ever leaving French territory.', 7.2, 4.49029, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bzgPLB7efMohled42PIn6CcOTnO.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Kuyme-U9-es'),
(3513, 135595, 'Trade Of Innocents', 'Justice needs a hero', 2012, 'In the back streets of a tourist town in present-day Southeast Asia, we find a filthy cinder block room; a bed with soiled sheets; a little girl waits for the next man. Alex (Dermot Mulroney), a human trafficking investigator, plays the role of her next customer as he negotiates with the pimp for the use of the child. Claire (Mira Sorvino), Alex''s wife, is caught up in the flow of her new life in Southeast Asia and her role as a volunteer in an aftercare shelter for rescued girls where lives of local neighborhood girl''s freedoms and dignity are threatened. Parallel story lines intertwine and unfold twists against the backdrop of the dangerous human trafficking world, in a story of struggle, life, hope and redemption in the "TRADE of INNOCENTS."', 5.5, 2.204138, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fEr6rVOHpXpnBK2WRZZ1wn0PEF9.jpg', NULL),
(3514, 8982, 'The Protector', 'Vengeance Knows No Mercy', 2005, 'In Bangkok, the young Kham was raised by his father in the jungle with elephants as members of their family. When his old elephant and the baby Kern are stolen by criminals, Kham finds that the animals were sent to Sidney. He travels to Australia, where he locates the baby elephant in a restaurant owned by the evil Madame Rose, the leader of an international Thai mafia. With the support of the efficient Thai sergeant Mark, who was involved in a conspiracy, Kham fights to rescue the animal from the mobsters.', 6.8, 11.81832, 'th', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uKE9BxgtT5g2pE3ZKC7MnzsAbTZ.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4Pev6lkexo8'),
(3515, 89861, 'Stiff Upper Lips', '', 1998, 'Stiff Upper Lips is a broad parody of British period films, especially the lavish Merchant-Ivory productions of the ''eighties and early ''nineties. Although it specifically targets A Room with a View, Chariots of Fire, Maurice, A Passage to India, and many other films, in a more general way Stiff Upper Lips satirises popular perceptions of certain Edwardian traits: propriety, sexual repression, xenophobia, and class snobbery.', 10, 0.356495, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3BKL5t6z6kudeDmuwYiIF5dzAV8.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SVn8zPPn7xo'),
(3516, 455, 'Bend It Like Beckham', 'Sometimes, to follow your dreams... you''ve got to bend the rules!', 2002, 'Jess Bhamra, the daughter of a strict Indian couple in London, is not permitted to play organized soccer, even though she is 18. When Jess is playing for fun one day, her impressive skills are seen by Jules Paxton, who then convinces Jess to play for her semi-pro team. Jess uses elaborate excuses to hide her matches from her family while also dealing with her romantic feelings for her coach, Joe.', 6.2, 22.054546, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2dzSBmFWWqt8NbnubJKIWU21Y86.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oQb8ShgVjJA'),
(3517, 57022, 'Sunshine State', 'Greetings from ...', 2002, 'A woman and her new husband returns to her hometown roots in coastal northern Florida, and must deal with family, business, and encroaching real estate development.', 6, 4.245123, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8OsgdG53vzF5uC8pCE61SA1tiNF.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6jvyCKitGB4'),
(3518, 14351, 'Crossover', '', 2006, 'The clock strikes midnight, money changes hands, the crowd is on their feet, and the court is alive with fast-paced razzle-dazzle basketball. These players don''t play for a school or a pro team. They play for the street and it''s underground...way underground.', 4.2, 3.201886, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jMShqkxESzjcXWdhGJz65CPWi8L.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RbtoIP14EdY'),
(3519, 147767, 'Khiladi 786', '', 2012, 'The 8th installment in the Khiladi series.', 4.7, 0.114342, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/3chNHVi7j0jmUvJ1k7n2EYPfFmC.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=natBTp0x88M'),
(3520, 10664, '[REC]²', 'Fear Revisited', 2009, 'The action continues from [REC], with the medical officer and a SWAT team outfitted with video cameras are sent into the sealed off apartment to control the situation.', 6.4, 22.341461, 'es', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fJuIhJ5s8WGNZN3wuk9d84nMjXk.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XPNY-94UfG4'),
(3521, 55567, 'Standing Ovation', 'Dance - Sing - Dream', 2010, 'A group of young girls is competing in a nation teen music video competition.', 3.9, 0.305922, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tPd7dnvIgzkvM8XLyC4mQCq21T1.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yW0BCzM35vg'),
(3522, 9277, 'The Sting', '...all it takes is a little confidence.', 1973, 'Set in the 1930''s this intricate caper deals with an ambitious small-time crook and a veteran con man who seek revenge on a vicious crime lord who murdered one of their gang.', 7.9, 28.500914, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ckmYng37zey8INYf6d10cVgIG93.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_nAIb_J9T5M'),
(3523, 9443, 'Chariots of Fire', 'This is the story of two men who run, not to run, but to prove something to the world. They will sacrifice anything to achieve their goals... except their honor.', 1981, 'The true story of British athletes preparing for and competing in the 1924 Summer Olympics.', 6.8, 10.439971, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qnRaum8k0HqGRml2i7OawFqUtEb.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AawHrbzbuMI'),
(3524, 16186, 'Diary of a Mad Black Woman', 'Time heals the heart. Faith heals the rest.', 2005, 'Charles McCarter and his wife Helen are about to celebrate their 18th-wedding anniversary when Helen comes home to find her clothes packed up in a U-Haul van parked in the driveway. Charles is divorcing Her. Helen moves in with her grandmother Madea, an old woman who doesn''t take any lip from anyone. Madea helps Helen through these tough times by showing her what is really important in life.', 6.4, 3.784535, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/e3MijvcHaMppp6sxNawsuLQEHjc.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nFi0lV3fMRU'),
(3525, 7863, 'Shine', 'A true story of the mystery of music and the miracle of love', 1996, 'Pianist David Helfgott, driven by his father and teachers, has a breakdown. Years later he returns to the piano, to popular if not critical acclaim.', 7.3, 10.396305, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cbmThowj2XAW7lKlMAXmnhZvjGI.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vTt4Ar6pzO4'),
(3526, 138697, 'Don Jon', 'Everyone loves a happy ending.', 2013, 'A New Jersey guy dedicated to his family, friends, and church, develops unrealistic expectations from watching porn and works to find happiness and intimacy with his potential true love.', 5.9, 33.296684, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uh8bwvgGXeUKzdL4oSul9zxyTcd.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zAE6YFikffs'),
(3527, 11901, 'High Plains Drifter', 'Welcome to Hell', 1973, 'A gunfighting stranger comes to the small settlement of Lago. After gunning down three gunmen who tried to kill him, the townsfolk decide to hire the Stranger to hold off three outlaws who are on their way.', 7.4, 19.12724, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/AjkJCFkqanK1OZqiHxc6Kl2wPQO.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=be2mIVxDrr8'),
(3528, 1548, 'Ghost World', 'Accentuate the negative.', 2001, 'A quirky girl tries to figure out what to do now that she had graduated from high school, and forms a friendship with an eccentric 40-year-old record collector after playing a prank on him with her best friend.', 7.1, 14.072941, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kY6qxvCv9JOnxoNA46NoddjfQSL.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rq6AOc0ATnU'),
(3529, 11889, 'Iris', '', 2001, 'True story of the lifelong romance between novelist Iris Murdoch and her husband John Bayley, from their student days through her battle with Alzheimer''s disease.', 6.2, 2.714043, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pqtVPrv3xPLTUayC0bPruRjYWDF.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9NUbiDJiglA'),
(3530, 33155, 'Galaxina', 'She''s too good to be true...and too real to be otherwise.', 1980, 'Galaxina is a lifelike, voluptuous android who is assigned to oversee the operations of an intergalactic Space Police cruiser captained by incompetent Cornelius Butt. When a mission requires the ship''s crew to be placed in suspended animation for decades, Galaxina finds herself alone for many years, developing emotions and falling in love with the ship''s pilot, Thor.', 3.3, 2.141143, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6mfrAf6e52PSfpP0THrzQRr36mf.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j9yt40bIAe8'),
(3531, 5528, 'The Chorus', '', 2004, 'Set in 1940''s France, a new teacher at a school for disruptive boys gives hope and inspiration.', 7.5, 20.982454, 'fr', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hUl7gSvkGygyk9wt3zy5NqpC5bb.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QVtJgU6WTj8'),
(3532, 321, 'Mambo Italiano', 'Things change. Family doesn''t.', 2003, 'A sweet comic film about an Italian man who comes out of the closet and the affect it has on his life and his crazy family. A family movie about the stereotypes of homosexuals and Italians – called by critics "the gay" My Big Fat Greek Wedding.', 5.6, 2.080741, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/usuEb1teTxqkK1wx54SmbdXltcN.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fw8s2TGeJSY'),
(3533, 4997, 'Wonderland', 'Sex, drugs, murder. Welcome to L.A.', 2003, 'On the afternoon of July 1, 1981, Los Angeles police responded to a distress call on Wonderland Avenue and discovered a grisly quadruple homicide. The police investigation that followed uncovered two versions of the events leading up to the brutal murders - both involving legendary porn actor John Holmes. You''re about to experience both versions.', 6.2, 7.79068, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mfG8S7D4rYeVqvTzjc3D36PAK3R.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tIWMOSKKlgs'),
(3534, 925, 'Do the Right Thing', 'It''s the hottest day of the summer. You can do nothing, you can do something, or you can...', 1989, 'On the hottest day of the year on a street in the Bedford-Stuyvesant section of Brooklyn, everyone''s hate and bigotry smolders and builds until it explodes into violence.', 7.6, 15.580335, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/63rmSDPahrH7C1gEFYzRuIBAN9W.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yVAD4fYRcvA'),
(3535, 27451, 'Harvard Man', 'Passion, Seduction, Deception.', 2001, 'College has always been a time for experimentation, sexual, cultural and otherwise. "Harvard Man" plays out against a background of love, sex, basketball, crime and experimentation. Action and philosophy in young people''s quest to discover their true identity.', 4.8, 5.336243, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vxZG1UXh8gA3nYmrPNUWCHGGBFn.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CidMaD84sjc'),
(3536, 73532, 'Le Havre', '', 2011, 'Marcel Marx, a former bohemian and struggling author, has given up his literary ambitions and relocated to the port city Le Havre. He leads a simple life based around his wife Arletty, his favourite bar and his not too profitable profession as a shoeshiner. As Arletty suddenly becomes seriously ill, Marcel''s path crosses with an underage illegal immigrant from Africa, who needs Marcel''s help to hide from the police.', 6.8, 10.787322, 'fr', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zCoGiKr8hn9fPYnxECjUhpaP8TI.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpAFPgNyxmc'),
(3537, 979, 'Irreversible', 'Time destroys everything.', 2002, 'Events over the course of one traumatic night in Paris unfold in reverse-chronological order as the beautiful Alex is brutally raped and beaten by a stranger in the underpass. Her boyfriend and ex-lover take matters into their own hands by hiring two criminals to help them find the rapist so that they can exact revenge. A simultaneously beautiful and terrible examination of the destructive nature of cause and effect, and how time destroys everything.', 7.1, 32.476097, 'fr', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rxeDxo8FvZpLu6iplNpxdtAVnfu.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e9D7hvIwgj4'),
(3538, 193722, 'R100', 'M For Father', 2013, 'Ruthless dominatrixes pursue a mild-mannered salesman who wants to get out of his unbreakable contract with a secret bondage club.', 5.4, 3.21392, 'ja', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qFdPIMXSBraNyMWwrWvYtJ9fT8g.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bfcvdZSvyIc'),
(3539, 7913, 'Rang De Basanti', 'A Generation Awakens', 2006, 'A young idealistic English filmmaker, Sue, arrives in India to make a film on Indian revolutionaries Bhagat Singh, Chandrashekhar Azad and their contemporaries and their fight for freedom from the British Raj. Owing to a lack of funds, she recruits students from Delhi University to act in her docu-drama. She finds DJ, who passed out five years back but still wants to be a part of the University because he doesn''t think there''s too much out there in the real world to look forward to. Karan, the son of Industrialist Rajnath Singhania, who shares an uncomfortable relationship with his father, but continues to live off him, albeit very grudgingly. Aslam, is a middle class Muslim boy, who lives in the by-lanes near Jama Masjid, poet, philosopher and guide to his friends. Sukhi, the group''s baby, innocent, vulnerable and with a weakness for only one thing - girls. Laxman Pandey...', 7.2, 5.206967, 'hi', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/f1bF8CHzEu621bPSIg6XiUNAabh.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=l-BTOTtcGmk'),
(3540, 253253, 'Animals', '', 2014, 'ANIMALS tells the story of Jude and Bobbie: a young couple that exist somewhere between homelessness and the fantasy of their imaginations. Though they masterfully con and steal in an attempt to stay one step ahead of their addiction, they are ultimately forced to face the reality of their situation when one of them gets hospitalized.', 6.2, 1.5846, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2mwMeQ5SEmw1cEUBVYEtP3helTo.jpg', NULL),
(3541, 51995, 'Salvation Boulevard', 'Faith alone doesn’t cut it anymore', 2011, 'Set in the world of mega-churches in which a former Deadhead-turned-born again-Christian finds himself on the run from fundamentalist members of his mega-church who will do anything to protect their larger-than-life pastor.', 5.6, 3.653305, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/q8kPPcpPUGhdAOP5LYHDMKZBXYP.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TYiYHfciJwE'),
(3542, 13173, 'The Ten', 'If He''d meant the commandments literally, He''d have written them in stone.', 2007, 'Ten stories, each inspired by one of the ten commandments.', 4.9, 3.865122, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/byhpbEcL1tuoNhU3x5vYF45QM8X.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m6pnqyDTUL0'),
(3543, 22908, 'A Room for Romeo Brass', '', 1999, 'Two twelve-year-old boys, Romeo and Gavin, undergo an extraordinary test of character and friendship when Morell, a naive but eccentric and dangerous stranger, comes between them. Morell befriends with the two boys and later asks them to help him pursue Romeo''s beautiful elder sister. He gradually becomes more violent after she rejects him.', 7.3, 1.391958, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gLpv2UUf5We4sXDKdo11aFfnKgw.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QhuD5cF9bBs'),
(3544, 70670, 'Headhunters', 'The hunt is on.', 2011, 'An accomplished headhunter risks everything to obtain a valuable painting owned by a former mercenary..', 7.1, 20.821846, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ll32Hyillq6VSC1F7v4m2uZjGKI.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MBjn4tdxC00'),
(3545, 84204, 'Grabbers', 'For the locals on Erin Island, it''s last orders.', 2012, 'Something sinister has come to the shores of Erin Island, unbeknownst to the quaint population of this sleepy fishing village resting somewhere off Ireland’s coast. First, some fishermen go missing. Then there is the rash of whale carcasses suddenly washing up on the beach. When the murders start, it’s up to two mismatched cops – an irresponsible alcoholic and his new partner, a by-the-book woman from the mainland – to protect the townsfolk from the giant, bloodsucking, tentacled aliens that prey upon them. Their only weapon, they discover, is booze. If they want to survive the creatures’ onslaught, everyone will have to get very, very drunk!', 6, 9.451228, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/n1CkFfuDCh4NDZgaXmyna3V0Hxc.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4e3izWdh9WM'),
(3546, 25248, 'Saint Ralph', 'He''s hoping for a miracle. He doesn''t have a prayer.', 2004, 'This Canadian made comedy/drama, set in Hamilton, Ontario in 1954, is a sweet and - at times - goofy story that becomes increasingly poignant as the minutes tick by.
INSERT INTO "public"."movies" ("id", "tmdb_id", "title", "tagline", "release_year", "overview", "score", "popularity", "language", "poster_url", "trailer_url") VALUES
(3993, 11072, 'Blazing Saddles', 'Never give a saga an even break!', 1974, 'A town – where everyone seems to be named Johnson – is in the way of the railroad and, in order to grab their land, Hedley Lemar, a politically connected nasty person, sends in his henchmen to make the town unlivable. After the sheriff is killed, the town demands a new sheriff from the Governor, so Hedley convinces him to send the town the first black sheriff in the west.', 7.2, 22.793928, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vNw1gOEDdYTDeNMuuq8OmiEHrfH.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tb2fYUKJdN8'),
(3994, 9730, 'Friday the 13th: The Final Chapter', 'Jason''s Back, and this is the one you''ve been screaming for.', 1984, 'After the Crystal Lake Massacres, Jason is pronounced dead and taken to the hospital morgue, where he is mysteriously revived, allowing his diabolical killing spree to continue at the camp where the gruesome slaughtering began. But this time, in addition to terrified teenagers, he meets a young boy named Tommy who has a special talent for horror masks and make up, leading up to a horrifying, bloody battle! Has Jason finally met his match?', 5.9, 14.013414, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1J7zudfR3VLPwAf9lK5YPfSu0n6.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OpWpe8REbag'),
(3995, 209274, 'Ida', '', 2013, 'Poland, 1962. Anna is a novice, an orphan brought up by nuns in a convent. Before she takes her vows, she is determined to see Wanda, her only living relative. Wanda tells Anna that Anna is Jewish. Both women embark on a journey not only to discover their tragic family story, but who they really are and where they belong, questioning their religions and beliefs.', 7.1, 13.265432, 'pl', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rQnBiFyHeSDxSaIgZpDaK52lflZ.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i_vrlpWB4Vo'),
(3996, 26371, 'Maurice', '', 1987, 'After his lover rejects him, a young man trapped by the oppressiveness of Edwardian society tries to come to terms with and accept his sexuality.', 7.1, 11.552247, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4MI2y8XViPrDiKs1p0QC4bTeZzf.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mzj8v3J-Fxo'),
(3997, 14137, 'Beer League', 'No Gut... No Glory.', 2006, 'An unemployed slacker (Lange) inspires his softball teammates to improve their game so they won''t get kicked out of the local league.', 5.3, 1.73892, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/yoB3G8yGNLHdbr4TSKZqRp7UJ72.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AaTvl23xRpA'),
(3998, 291, 'Riding Giants', '', 2004, 'Riding Giants is story about big wave surfers who have become heroes and legends in their sport. Directed by the skateboard guru Stacy Peralta.', 7.6, 0.895946, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8L3ir0KNqSqpps2oVAeCUPVTPhr.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ADy8f6t4Ri8'),
(3999, 14139, 'Timecrimes', 'A trip back in time from the present to...', 2007, 'A man accidentally gets into a time machine and travels back in time nearly an hour. Finding himself will be the first of a series of disasters of unforeseeable consequences.', 7, 19.02965, 'es', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zdxQRP7mzczMJBwKnv8MCPRq7rQ.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3XuWoe9NSic'),
(4000, 33106, 'Silver Medalist', '', 2009, 'An action-adventure story focused on the lives of express deliverymen, traffic cops and lonely beauties.', 7.4, 0.406645, 'zh', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ggTqQBLLiDx2MRBp4q3hOPsXDcV.jpg', NULL);
INSERT INTO "public"."movies" ("id", "tmdb_id", "title", "tagline", "release_year", "overview", "score", "popularity", "language", "poster_url", "trailer_url") VALUES
(4001, 8875, 'Timber Falls', '', 2007, 'A weekend of camping in the mountains becomes an excursion into hell for a young couple, who become pawns in a grotesque plot hatched by deranged locals.', 5.2, 3.687574, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/v6Lgqh0OYLpeKzbIqxPeDXYstKE.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xo70gmH2wjg'),
(4002, 872, 'Singin'' in the Rain', 'What a Glorious Feeling!', 1952, 'In 1927 Hollywood, Don Lockwood and Lina Lamont are a famous on-screen romantic pair in silent movies, but Lina mistakes the on-screen romance for real love. When their latest film is transformed into a musical, Don has the perfect voice for the songs, but strident voice faces the studio to dub her voice. Aspiring actress, Kathy Selden is brought in and, while she is working on the movie, Don falls in love with her.', 7.8, 36.556953, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/w03EiJVHP8Un77boQeE7hg9DVdU.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lSE8sl2-PZg'),
(4003, 72914, 'Fat, Sick & Nearly Dead', 'FAT, SICK & NEARLY DEAD is an inspiring film that chronicles Joe''s personal mission to regain his health.', 2010, '100 pounds overweight, loaded up on steroids and suffering from a debilitating autoimmune disease, Joe Cross is at the end of his rope and the end of his hope. In the mirror he saw a 310lb man whose gut was bigger than a beach ball and a path laid out before him that wouldn''t end well— with one foot already in the grave, the other wasn''t far behind. FAT, SICK &amp; NEARLY DEAD is an inspiring film that chronicles Joe''s personal mission to regain his health.', 7.1, 0.545825, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/yKXRwMValA4ZbCaC68ANO24ALcY.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x9SGWcZwk7c'),
(4004, 139038, 'A Haunted House', 'This $*%! ain''t paranormal.', 2013, 'A spoof of all the "found-footage/documentary style" films released in recent years.', 5.4, 18.661541, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tpw6kvuAJBo1CGRw1Bwdz1KU0hc.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=daCqXHagaPY'),
(4005, 126509, '2016: Obama''s America', 'Love Him, Hate Him, You Don''t Know Him', 2012, '2016: Obama''s America takes audiences on a gripping visual journey into the heart of the worlds most powerful office to reveal the struggle of whether one man''s past will redefine America over the next four years. The film examines the question, "If Obama wins a second term, where will we be in 2016?"  Across the globe and in America, people in 2008 hungered for a leader who would unite and lift us from economic turmoil and war. True to Americas ideals, they invested their hope in a new kind of president, Barack Obama. What they didn''t know is that Obama is a man with a past, and in powerful ways that past defines him--who he is, how he thinks, and where he intends to take America and the world. Immersed in exotic locales across four continents, best selling author Dinesh DSouza races against time to find answers to Obama''s past and reveal where America will be in 2016.', 4.6, 0.973582, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9Ht3rh0GVgh0rGqW99wCXWE4DP1.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vtv6XUT-hno'),
(4006, 9591, 'That Thing You Do!', 'In every life there comes a time when that dream you dream becomes that thing you do.', 1996, 'A Pennsylvania band scores a hit in 1964 and rides the star-making machinery as long as it can, with lots of help from its manager.', 6.8, 14.885388, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9RmZu33qHdyZFGLfhEOmkTjdNEu.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NjxU0Q3r73Y'),
(4007, 10676, 'Halloween III: Season of the Witch', '...and now the earth will run with blood again!', 1982, 'Dr. Daniel Challis and Ellie Grimbridge stumble onto a gruesome murder scheme when Ellie''s novelty-salesman father, Harry, is killed while in possession of a strange mask made by the Silver Shamrock mask company. The company''s owner, Conal Cochran, wants to return Halloween to its darker roots using his masks -- and his unspeakable scheme would unleash death and destruction across the country.', 5, 12.030456, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/WABfdeaThFYXCySGIOvRNv2sSW.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kk8QJdD5ExE'),
(4008, 1687, 'Escape from the Planet of the Apes', 'Meet baby Milo who has Washington terrified.', 1971, 'The world is shocked by the appearance of two talking chimpanzees, who arrived mysteriously in a U.S. spacecraft. They become the toast of society; but one man believes them to be a threat to the human race.', 6.3, 18.30961, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/AnbLVdUEroTfHTUVAJCxkL4R0IH.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2e1acuBXj4g'),
(4009, 24748, 'Hud', 'The man with the barbed-wire soul.', 1963, 'Hud Bannon is a ruthless young man who tarnishes everything and everyone he touches. Hud represents the perfect embodiment of alienated youth, out for kicks with no regard for the consequences. There is bitter conflict between the callous Hud and his stern and highly principled father, Homer. Hud''s nephew Lon admires Hud''s cheating ways, though he soon becomes too aware of Hud''s reckless amorality to bear him anymore. In the world of the takers and the taken, Hud is a winner. He''s a cheat, but, he explains, "I always say the law was meant to be interpreted in a lenient manner."', 7.5, 6.82919, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/A168bF52vmAIGkC2Qafj7M2EmaE.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Uly7FC5EDjw'),
(4010, 181330, 'Kevin Hart: Let Me Explain', 'Witness the rise of a legend', 2013, 'Captures the laughter, energy and mayhem from Hart''s 2012 "Let Me Explain" concert tour, which spanned 10 countries and 80 cities, and generated over $32 million in ticket sales.', 7.1, 9.799357, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lzYQkVuEN0zw2JvJsMUsOU47nb4.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uX0N972soEg'),
(4011, 468, 'My Own Private Idaho', 'It''s not where you go, it''s how you get there.', 1991, 'In this loose adaptation of Shakespeare''s "Henry IV," Mike Waters (River Phoenix) is a gay hustler afflicted with narcolepsy. Scott Favor (Keanu Reeves) is the rebellious son of a mayor. Together, the two travel from Portland, Oregon to Idaho and finally to the coast of Italy in a quest to find Mike''s estranged mother. Along the way they turn tricks for money and drugs, eventually attracting the attention of a wealthy benefactor and sexual deviant.', 7.1, 10.363642, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/p9TF90Pb5yg2MNb2UztzyXktMm4.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t2Xnv2nV0lI'),
(4012, 401, 'Garden State', '', 2004, 'Andrew returns to his hometown for the funeral of his mother, a journey that reconnects him with past friends. The trip coincides with his decision to stop taking his powerful antidepressants. A chance meeting with Sam - a girl also suffering from various maladies - opens up the possibility of rekindling emotional attachments, confronting his psychologist father, and perhaps beginning a new life.', 7.1, 30.58396, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/h3iqYiGS6F3y7GxaS4AT8nFxZ2i.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u82n0e1mgmQ'),
(4013, 76, 'Before Sunrise', 'Can the greatest romance of your life last only one night?', 1995, 'A dialogue marathon of a film, this fairytale love story of an American boy and French girl. During a day and a night together in Vienna their two hearts collide.', 7.7, 23.672571, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kf1Jb1c2JAOqjuzA3H4oDM263uB.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jGvcbSabADM'),
(4014, 50538, 'Evil Words', '', 2003, 'One day, for no apparent reason, a cop kills 11 children. The same day, horror novelist Thomas Roy tries to commit suicide after cutting his fingers. At first glance, nothing seems to link the two events – until Dr. Paul Lacasse, a disillusioned psychiatrist, takes over the case. Prompted by his colleague Jeanne, a fan of Thomas Roy, Dr. Lacasse investigates the writer’s past. Hounded by a gossip columnist, Dr. Lacasse uncovers a series of troubling facts that bolster his convictions about the case. As he tries to reassemble the pieces of the puzzle in order to better treat the famous writer, Dr. Lacasse is dragged further and further into a series of events, with terrifying consequences.', 6.9, 0.205034, 'fr', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cwH7X2Gaf07nNnTDfD2VvIMtN5D.jpg', NULL),
(4015, 25636, 'Jesus'' Son', '', 1999, 'A young man turns from drug addiction and petty crime to a life redeemed by a discovery of compassion', 6.7, 5.581743, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/A2lVDbF1oTuCMlh69vLnqugWEAM.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Tc0cb4sEMvU'),
(4016, 19316, 'Saving Face', 'A romantic comedy about right, wrong and everything in between.', 2004, 'A Chinese-American lesbian and her traditionalist mother are reluctant to go public with secret loves that clash against cultural expectations.', 6.8, 2.487255, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7XbbgkKi4nEMOu9iwiANXpjKKhe.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=78h8WeP3Oas'),
(4017, 21074, 'Brick Lane', '', 2007, 'The grind of daily life as a Brick Lane Bangladessi as seen through the eyes of Nazneen (Chatterjee), who at 17 enters an arranged marriage with Chanu (Kaushik). Years later, living in east London with her family, she meets a young man Karim (Simpson).', 5.2, 0.262135, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fOi0il1YvBj0d6wE5OyGIqMPV4S.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NhRs8GeWzGM'),
(4018, 84329, 'Robot & Frank', 'Friendship doesn''t have an off switch', 2012, 'A delightful dramatic comedy, a buddy picture, and, for good measure, a heist film. Curmudgeonly old Frank lives by himself. His routine involves daily visits to his local library, where he has a twinkle in his eye for the librarian. His grown children are concerned about their father’s well-being and buy him a caretaker robot. Initially resistant to the idea, Frank soon appreciates the benefits of robotic support – like nutritious meals and a clean house – and eventually begins to treat his robot like a true companion. With his robot’s assistance, Frank’s passion for his old, unlawful profession is reignited, for better or worse.', 6.8, 23.419062, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/602vUwe1GPmaRvcrT3OQWqH1Nm1.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a_gAJk_CfPI'),
(4019, 20, 'My Life Without Me', '', 2003, 'A Pedro Almodovar production in which a fatally ill mother with only two months to live creates a list of things she wants to do before she dies with out telling her family of her illness.', 7.2, 7.958831, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pFEtVPW88pWflYV84UFL0h1iJr3.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rxPRhy276ls'),
(4020, 157386, 'The Spectacular Now', 'From the Writers of (500) Days of Summer', 2013, 'A hard-partying high school senior''s philosophy on life changes when he meets the not-so-typical "nice girl."', 6.8, 25.722748, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tYDbDuZ3K4Xwp3cwtmZM6k53bwq.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0dCfbBwFI2Y'),
(4021, 13007, 'Religulous', 'Heaven help us.', 2008, 'Commentator-comic Bill Maher plays devil''s advocate with religion as he talks to believers about their faith. Traveling around the world, Maher examines the tenets of Christianity, Judaism and Islam and raises questions about homosexuality, proof of Christ''s existence, Jewish Sabbath laws, violent Muslim extremists.', 7.2, 9.774126, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hBv5LCbWxPB8iU77dwurSGMVZ3N.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XdkyLrDpaUg'),
(4022, 13518, 'Fuel', '', 2008, 'Record high oil prices, global warming, and an insatiable demand for energy: these issues define our generation. The film exposes shocking connections between the auto industry, the oil industry, and the government, while exploring alternative energies such as solar, wind, electricity, and non-food-based biofuels.', 7, 0.197469, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fg88f3Nis36udZAEryzB1iQ1iYo.jpg', NULL),
(4023, 116584, 'Valley of the Heart''s Delight', 'The roar of the mob drowned out the truth.', 2006, 'When a fatal kidnapping ignites a firestorm of suspicion and rage in idyllic 1933 San Jose, California, a hard-nosed young reporter takes on the powers-that-be to prevent the lynching of two men he believes are innocent.', 7, 0.142255, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/WTohWlSGwFNDfjJJtyPMraH3qo.jpg', NULL),
(4024, 46849, 'Eye of the Dolphin', 'She found her voice in the ocean... And within herself.', 2007, 'Alyssa is a troubled 14-year old, suspended from school a year after her mother has drowned. Her grandmother Lucy, at wit''s end, decides to take Alyssa to her father, James, whom Alyssa thought was dead for years. He studies dolphin communication at Smith''s Point, on the Grand Bahama Island. James has not known of Alyssa''s existence and is clueless about parenthood. The women arrive at the same time that James may lose his research operation to a tourist attraction. Father, daughter, dolphins, and town are on a collision course. Alyssa and James get encouragement from James''s girlfriend and her father. It''s the dolphins who can teach, and Alyssa who discovers how to listen.', 7.1, 0.301884, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8oaWtuz9pfRtCOtHQ5KIWB3vnYP.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n07tQzv-NhM'),
(4025, 40428, '8: The Mormon Proposition', 'Equality for some.', 2010, 'Filmmaker and ex-Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints member Reed Cowan examines that church''s nationwide efforts to prevent the legalization of gay marriage - including California''s Proposition 8, which was passed by voters in 2008. Confidential church documents, statements by high-ranking church officials and other sources detail 30 years of efforts to turn back gay rights, particularly by the Mormon-sponsored National Organization for Marriage.', 5.5, 0.424957, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/glTnodgy1tZa794mnETfHjCPekC.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ezwIZo-hKiI'),
(4026, 17334, 'The Other End of the Line', '', 2008, 'An employee at an Indian call-center travels to San Francisco to be with a guy she falls for over the phone', 6.1, 3.393648, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uiLgARBzUiE7PPRiJILXSh4zOIW.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q2HB-SgCTq4'),
(4027, 1698, 'Anatomy', 'Some study. Some are studied.', 2000, 'Medical student Paula Henning wins a place at an exclusive Heidelberg medical school. When the body of a young man she met on the train turns up on her dissection table, she begins to investigate the mysterious circumstances surrounding his death, and uncovers a gruesome conspiracy perpetrated by an Antihippocratic secret society operating within the school.', 6.1, 5.025938, 'de', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hZgnRhrOkmjjod5u3umbw4y08kX.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0nXtQ5QIF6o'),
(4028, 20764, 'Sleep Dealer', 'Crossing the border just got easier. Plug into the new American dream.', 2008, 'Set in a near-future, militarized world marked by closed borders, virtual labor and a global digital network that joins minds and experiences, three strangers risk their lives to connect with each other and break the barriers of technology.', 6, 4.624691, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kFXQ4oMJkXAWjyo7Tr5GrLjmk61.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xW8oSRSzS7M'),
