(4332, 277685, 'Unfriended', 'Online, your memories last forever. But so do your mistakes.', 2015, 'While video chatting one night, six high school friends receive a Skype message from a classmate who killed herself exactly one year ago. A first they think it''s a prank, but when the girl starts revealing the friends'' darkest secrets, they realize they are dealing with something out of this world, something that wants them dead. Told entirely from a young girl''s computer desktop, Unfriended redefines ''found footage'' for a new generation of teens.', 5.5, 41.97233, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8byPxREr3BqBNyyij5WHVSOVtYk.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Lgj4GjqCFlY'),
