(4691, 21334, 'Children of Heaven', 'A Little Secret...Their Biggest Adventure!', 1997, 'Zohre''s shoes are gone; her older brother Ali lost them. They are poor, there are no shoes for Zohre until they come up with an idea: they will share one pair of shoes, Ali''s. School awaits...', 7.8, 7.072118, 'fa', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jWqh1CJWAEcxckMRrf6ARhIEh0R.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dqxvZeQsVzY'),
(4692, 79120, 'Weekend', 'A (sort of) love story between two guys over a cold weekend in October.', 2011, 'After a drunken house party with his straight mates, Russell heads out to a gay club. Just before closing time he picks up Glen but what''s expected to be just a one-night stand becomes something else, something special.', 7.4, 1.041254, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ksg3QX2iMLzEkvS6AwIGh5A9CXT.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2IFbcWG1F9o'),
(4693, 27995, 'She''s Gotta Have It', 'A Seriously Sexy Comedy', 1986, 'The story of Nola Darling''s simultaneous sexual relationships with three different men is told by her and by her partners and other friends. All three men wanted her to commit solely to them; Nola resists being "owned" by a single partner.', 6.1, 6.722213, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qiJuXvPONqTSSnzhbCBqE7EotV.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Pd9oTGr_1DA'),
(4694, 253290, 'Butterfly Girl', '', 2014, 'Abbie came of age in honky tonks, defying her life threatening disease, but all the while longing for an identity of her own. Now that she is 18, how much is she willing to sacrifice for her independence?', 0, 0.015189, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/nQRsj3wRXOesAaN0I31rSNz2WX7.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FNfc_oBUE6E'),
(4695, 344466, 'The World Is Mine', '', 2015, 'Larisa is 16 and lives in a city by the sea. It''s a small city, where gossip and news spread fast. It''s a city where your image and influence, "manelele", money and power are all that matters. And Larisa… wants it all. And even if she doesn''t have it, she fights for it. Larisa believes in herself. She knows that she deserves better. She is convinced that it''s worth doing everything it takes to fulfill her dreams. And for her courage and recklessness - we love her.', 0, 0.327622, 'ro', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/emdjO6Bl71aOirfNh0OcPdyKp5Q.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rt9_JB5Xk4w'),
