(3229, 11176, 'The Muppet Movie', 'More entertaining than humanly possible.', 1979, 'Kermit the Frog is persuaded by agent Dom DeLuise to pursue a career in Hollywood. Along the way, Kermit picks up Fozzie Bear, Miss Piggy, Gonzo, and a motley crew of other Muppets with similar aspirations. Meanwhile, Kermit must elude the grasp of a frog-leg restaurant magnate.', 7, 10.639916, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8LUjnIW5ph6pHoXDE3Zg4iVi6BV.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qDfXXaqfc2k'),
