(3236, 170, '28 Days Later', 'His fear began when he woke up alone. His terror began when he realised he wasn''t.', 2002, 'Twenty-eight days after a killer virus was accidentally unleashed from a British research facility, a small group of London survivors are caught in a desperate struggle to protect themselves from the infected. Carried by animals and humans, the virus turns those it infects into homicidal maniacs -- and it''s absolutely impossible to contain.', 7.1, 45.490376, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sQckQRt17VaWbo39GIu0TMOiszq.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mWEhfF27O0c'),
