(3238, 10734, 'Escape from Alcatraz', 'No one has ever escaped from Alcatraz...and no one ever will!', 1979, 'Escape from Alcatraz tells the story of the only three men ever to escape from the infamous maximum security prison at Alcatraz. In 29 years, the seemingly impenetrable federal penitentiary, which housed Al Capone and "Birdman" Robert Stroud, was only broken once - by three men never heard of again.', 7.2, 26.356697, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uORr2GXQnyqgBOg6tVsRCJD2qxc.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5bLmGl_USn8'),
(3239, 37964, 'Brown Sugar', 'When did you first fall in love with hip-hop?', 2002, 'Sidney is a writer who''s just left her L.A. Times music review gig to edit New York hip-hop magazine XXL. Dre is an executive with a hip-hop record company based in New York. They''ve known each other since they met as children, when both discovered hip-hop for the first time. Now that they''re back together, they should be perfect for each other, except that Dre''s about to marry lawyer Reese and Sidney claims not to be interested in Dre romantically. Meanwhile, Dre is growing increasingly restless with his company''s focus on profit over artistry, which leads to signing the gimmicky duo Ren and Ten while ignoring the talented Chris', 7, 3.501158, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hKltNdfxKg28mOgFwizNyhIFkJ2.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1cMkcfL8w5k'),
(3240, 28121, 'A Thin Line Between Love and Hate', 'When you play, you pay.', 1996, 'Nightclub manager Darnell Wright is a perpetual playboy who is almost as devoted to his job as he is to the pursuit of beautiful women. After he sets his sights on the ultra-classy Brandi Web, he launches an all-out assault to win her heart. Ultimately, charm, lust and passion prevail, but Darnell learns the hard way that when you play, you pay. Brandi is much harder to get rid of than she was to get--especially when she realizes that she has a rival vying for Darnell''s affection. When he finally decides to call it quits, Brandi becomes an obsessed femme fatale stalking the new love of her life.', 5.7, 2.088251, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wo9AGi5LlFXZUj8MDPq3eKCUMpd.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E3DxV5-ASsI'),
(3241, 40807, '50/50', 'It takes a pair to beat the odds.', 2011, 'Inspired by a true story, a comedy centered on a 27-year-old guy who learns of his cancer diagnosis, and his subsequent struggle to beat the disease.', 7, 33.37283, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8f9tM9JVB4ETBhxlQcXIjLckArl.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pVObFYOU9rE'),
(3242, 10885, 'Shutter', 'The most terrifying images are the ones that are real.', 2008, 'A newly married couple discovers disturbing, ghostly images in photographs they develop after a tragic accident. Fearing the manifestations may be connected, they investigate and learn that some mysteries are better left unsolved.', 5.3, 8.864368, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bft6OyITsxSZuTxu2oJipApLran.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BSNg47ntpt8'),
