(3270, 13154, 'Showdown in Little Tokyo', 'One''s a warrior. One''s a wise guy. They''re two L.A. cops going after a gang of drug lords. Feet first.', 1991, 'An American with a Japanese upbringing, Chris Kenner is a police officer assigned to the Little Tokyo section of Los Angeles. Kenner is partnered with Johnny Murata, a Japanese-American who isn''t in touch with his roots. Despite their differences, both men excel at martial arts, and utilize their formidable skills when they go up against Yoshida, a vicious yakuza drug dealer with ties to Kenner''s past.', 5.7, 8.403859, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/phwuQrs557cJkRhoS1TVWsslnJK.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DsIdfBA51bQ'),
(3271, 26618, 'Clay Pigeons', 'Some killers are strange, some are deranged, and some are just plain psycho.', 1998, 'Clay is a young man in a small town who witnesses his friend, Earl kill himself because of the ongoing affair that Clay was having with the man''s wife, Amanda. Feeling guilty, Clay now resists the widow when she presses him to continue with their sexual affairs. Clay inadvertently befriends a serial killer named Lester Long, who murders the widow in an attempt to "help" his "fishing buddy."', 6.3, 4.221313, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/A6ebyxABDaLvOBaS6Q6MWCdOsY5.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VChKGXLiLYI'),
