(3443, 642, 'Butch Cassidy and the Sundance Kid', 'Not that it matters, but most of it is true.', 1969, 'In late 1890s Wyoming, Butch Cassidy is the affable, clever and talkative leader of the outlaw Hole in the Wall Gang. His closest companion is the laconic dead-shot ''Sundance Kid''. As the west rapidly becomes civilized, the law finally catches up to Butch, Sundance and their gang.  Chased doggedly by a special posse, the two decide to make their way to South America in hopes of evading their pursuers once and for all.', 7.4, 24.499996, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gFmmykF1Ym3OGzENo50nZQaD1dx.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YdJW2UxvSFQ'),
(3444, 433, 'Mary Poppins', 'It''s supercalifragilisticexpialidocious!', 1964, 'The movie combines a diverting story, songs, color and sequences of live action blended with the movements of animated figures. Mary Poppins is a kind of Super-nanny who flies in with her umbrella in response to the request of the Banks children and proceeds to put things right with the aid of her rather extraordinary magical powers before flying off again.', 7.4, 59.96152, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1DjJh0vwGwi6KugPZfDiliO25XP.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H54Ft85U2RA'),
(3445, 16619, 'Ordinary People', 'Everything is in its proper place...except the past.', 1980, 'Beth, Calvin, and their son Conrad are living in the aftermath of the death of the other son. Conrad is overcome by grief and misplaced guilt to the extent of a suicide attempt. He is in therapy. Beth had always preferred his brother and is having difficulty being supportive to Conrad. Calvin is trapped between the two trying to hold the family together.', 7.4, 12.541983, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8CFPYcRatQFFysCjQanqYMQyS2Y.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vtpsjMEGbaE'),
(3446, 1725, 'West Side Story', 'The screen achieves one of the great entertainments in the history of motion pictures', 1961, 'In the slums of the upper West Side of Manhattan, New York, a gang of Polish-American teenagers called the Jets compete with a rival gang of recently immigrated Puerto Ricans, the Sharks, to "own" the neighborhood streets. Tensions are high between the gangs but two kids, one from each rival gang, fall in love leading to tragedy.', 7, 23.431116, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vCtErvzF6S93DtoD7URwy9Mr7oe.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HpKbrpPiExA'),
(3447, 11977, 'Caddyshack', 'The snobs against the slobs!', 1980, 'At an exclusive country club, an ambitious young caddy, Danny Noonan, eagerly pursues a caddy scholarship in hopes of attending college and, in turn, avoiding a job at the lumber yard. In order to succeed, he must first win the favour of the elitist Judge Smails, and then the caddy golf tournament which Smails sponsors.', 6.6, 15.929648, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lXnNz7zOXCsftMDVoU3VSo0Eioi.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vKlecXacidE'),
(3448, 20322, 'The Brothers', '', 2001, 'This is the story of four African-American "yuppies" (a banker, a doctor, a lawyer, and a "playboy") who call themselves "The Brothers". When the playboy gets engaged, the other three friends find themselves having to come to terms with their own issues of commitment and honesty...', 6.5, 3.029944, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/342I0mOBCNTzx4ls4GvIagfzu2m.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X0_ttpqt6nc'),
(3449, 16158, 'The Wood', 'From best friends to best men.', 1999, 'In the panicky, uncertain hours before his wedding, a groom with prenuptial jitters and his two best friends reminisce about growing up together in the middle-class African-American neighborhood of Inglewood, California. Flashing back to the twenty-something trio''s childhood exploits, the memories capture the mood and nostalgia of the ''80s era.', 7.1, 5.537646, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/yEWMSJHkzMLgsTgsvR5TxuP3lBt.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=koP2IdQhA_I'),
(3450, 629, 'The Usual Suspects', 'Five Criminals. One Line Up. No Coincidence.', 1995, 'Held in an L.A. interrogation room, Verbal Kint attempts to convince the feds that a mythic crime lord, Keyser Soze, not only exists, but was also responsible for drawing him and his four partners into a multi-million dollar heist that ended with an explosion in San Pedro harbor – leaving few survivors. Verbal lures his interrogators with an incredible story of the crime lord''s almost supernatural prowess.', 8.1, 64.02503, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rWbsxdwF9qQzpTPCLmDfVnVqTK1.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jM3jrHGAsIE'),
(3451, 10160, 'A Nightmare on Elm Street 5: The Dream Child', 'Now Freddy’s a daddy, he’s killing for two.', 1989, 'Alice, having survived the previous installment of the Nightmare series, finds the deadly dreams of Freddy Krueger starting once again. This time, the taunting murderer is striking through the sleeping mind of Alice''s unborn child. His intention is to be "born again" into the real world. The only one who can stop Freddy is his dead mother, but can Alice free her spirit in time to save her own son?', 5.5, 12.654051, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6Mrk5SK017PjjOIokUbmX8Qkzf1.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LFm_jiI8RiA'),
(3452, 11452, 'National Lampoon’s Van Wilder', 'Don''t Graduate. Celebrate.', 2002, 'Van Wilder has been attending college for far too many years and is scared to graduate, but Van’s father eventually realizes what is going on. When he stops paying his son''s tuition fees, Van must come up with the money if he wants to stay in college, so he and his friends come up with a great fund-raising idea – throwing parties. However, when the college magazine finds out and reporter, Gwen is sent to do a story on Van Wilder, things get a little complicated.', 5.9, 35.108498, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hl19MAS9hV5QkkUdZuoLleDuNH9.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qShNioFXXwM'),
(3453, 12163, 'The Wrestler', 'Love. Pain. Glory.', 2008, 'Aging wrestler Randy "The Ram" Robinson is long past his prime but still ready and rarin'' to go on the pro-wrestling circuit. After a particularly brutal beating, however, Randy hangs up his tights, pursues a serious relationship with a long-in-the-tooth stripper, and tries to reconnect with his estranged daughter. But he can''t resist the lure of the ring and readies himself for a comeback.', 7.3, 40.196514, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6OTR8dSoNGjWohJNo3UhIGd3Tj.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qjhGZhRJ3j0'),
(3454, 32275, 'Duel in the Sun', 'Emotions . . . As Violent As The Wind-Swept Prairie !', 1946, 'Beautiful half-breed Pearl Chavez becomes the ward of her dead father''s first love and finds herself torn between her sons, one good and the other bad.', 6.2, 7.60445, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dW479xuDWrcuFuxr7yfoReztlzF.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OrP_CtoeO9E'),
(3455, 13785, 'Best in Show', 'Some pets deserve a little more respect than others.', 2000, 'The tension is palpable, the excitement is mounting and the heady scent of competition is in the air as hundreds of eager contestants from across America prepare to take part in what is undoubtedly one of the greatest events of their lives -- the Mayflower Dog Show. The canine contestants and their owners are as wondrously diverse as the great country that has bred them.', 6.7, 10.982255, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/qkYBCMN26SxkQww4gLxUXQm5vr4.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w7H9fsREWdg'),
(3456, 1103, 'Escape from New York', '1997. New York City is now a maximum security prison. Breaking out is impossible. Breaking in is insane.', 1981, 'In 1997, the island of Manhattan has been walled off and turned into a giant maximum security prison within which the country''s worst criminals are left to form their own anarchic society. However, when the President of the United States crash lands on the island, the authorities turn to a former soldier and current convict, Snake Plissken, to rescue him.', 6.9, 24.351305, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vH9llaphjAssRGi0k7e75tD40Ce.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bqT09APfNKI'),
(3457, 36739, 'School Daze', '', 1988, 'In the South of the United States are taking place confrontations between two groups of students who have different ideas and are not able to accept the one of the oponent.', 6.2, 3.159574, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vnfjKHcmah7ReMxLNF18JMXFgSZ.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=snxtT7xr-nY'),
(3458, 14144, 'Daddy Day Camp', 'The summer is going to be in tents.', 2007, 'Seeking to offer his son the satisfying summer camp experience that eluded him as a child, the operator of a neighborhood daycare center opens his own camp, only to face financial hardship and stiff competition from a rival camp.', 4.4, 12.601677, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fhuhSVb3j8SShe6FhnVUAfSRg6h.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fNibbOj7mOk'),
(3459, 10622, 'Mr. Nice Guy', 'Fight first. Apologize later.', 1997, 'A Chinese chef accidentally gets involved with a news reporter who filmed a drug bust that went awry and is now being chased by gangs who are trying to get the video tape.', 6.3, 7.077505, 'cn', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wAAt2gvbkbeefzjd06GPfkdfUho.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PznkKtrh6qo'),
(3460, 13370, 'A Mighty Wind', 'Back together for the first time, again.', 2003, 'In "A Mighty Wind", director Christopher Guest reunites the team from "Best In Show" and "Waiting for Guffman" to tell tell the story of 60''s-era folk musicians, who inspired by the death of their former manager, get back on the stage for one concert in New York City''s Town Hall.', 6.6, 4.053017, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5wUYwAD75BxtJ0Mp4da6XzHIFex.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-X9ZCW76-I8'),
(3461, 11191, 'Mystic Pizza', 'A Romantic Comedy With The Works', 1988, 'Three teenage girls come of age while working at a pizza parlor in Mystic Connecticut.', 5.9, 6.379933, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/bV3MvnUTgKlbGi7K1QaYNLhdOlM.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=phKgLzz15KQ'),
(3462, 10215, 'Sliding Doors', 'What if one split second sent your life in two completely different directions?.', 1998, 'Gwyneth Paltrow plays London publicist Helen, effortlessly sliding between parallel storylines that show what happens if she does or does not catch a train back to her apartment. Love. Romantic entanglements. Deception. Trust. Friendship. Comedy. All come into focus as the two stories shift back and forth, overlap and surprisingly converge.', 6.5, 15.639016, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/s8VOVTywXZIIHqdEjkCZziH0ebq.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Da-Mizk86AE'),
(3463, 25066, 'Tales from the Hood', 'Chill or be Chilled', 1995, 'A strange funeral director tells four strange tales of horror with an African American focus to three drug dealers he traps in his place of business.', 5.4, 3.89204, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/glPNCcI7V8zTTI3BG0iIUJJcwXN.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dOO-A59c4C0'),
(3464, 1523, 'The Last King of Scotland', 'Charming. Magnetic. Murderous.', 2006, 'Young Scottish doctor, Nicholas Garrigan decides it''s time for an adventure after he finishes his formal education, so he decides to try his luck in Uganda, and arrives during the downfall of President Obote. General Idi Amin comes to power and asks Garrigan to become his personal doctor.', 7.4, 26.286955, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/mTtgpH6UnHUtD8moRJUzfGLOZTj.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R_W7PC6NnN4'),
(3465, 11361, 'Halloween 5: The Revenge of Michael Myers', 'Michael Lives, And This Time They''re Ready!', 1989, 'Presumed dead after a shoot-out with the Haddonfield police, Michael Myers is secretly nursed back to health -- and returns a year later to kill again and once more targets his young niece, Jamie. Jamie is now recovering in the local children''s hospital after attacking her stepmother and losing her voice. Her mental link with her evil uncle may be the key to uprooting her family tree.', 5.2, 8.008844, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rYvP6yMXCIVHnkVtwGaAXFmpzkB.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UPwAtB65dCs'),
(3466, 92591, 'Bernie', 'A story so unbelievable it must be true.', 2012, 'In this true story in the tiny, rural town of Carthage, TX, assistant funeral director Bernie Tiede was one of the town''s most beloved residents. Everyone loved and appreciated Bernie, and it came as no surprise when he befriended Marjorie Nugent, an affluent widow who was as well known for her sour attitude as her fortune. Until that day news came that Marjorie Nugent had been dead for some time, and Bernie Tiede was being charged with the murder.', 6.5, 12.68514, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rW5CetooG545jpkPNpD4FjFAXfe.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pQ5YN5epsaw'),
(3467, 57612, 'Dolphins and Whales: Tribes of the Ocean', '', 2008, 'This documentary goes to coral reefs of the Bahamas and the waters of the Kingdom of Tonga for a close encounter with the surviving tribes of the ocean: wild dolphins and belugas, the love of a Humpback mother for her newborn calf, the singing Humpback males, an orca the mighty King of the ocean, and the gentle manatee. Little-known aspects of these creatures capable of sophisticated communication and social interaction. Documents the life of these graceful, majestic yet endangered sea creatures', 8, 0.041651, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gvrzdrxr69ZdzjfMQ4evhujAGbF.jpg', NULL),
(3468, 12509, 'Pollock', 'A true portrait of life and art.', 2000, 'In August of 1949, Life Magazine ran a banner headline that begged the question: "Jackson Pollock: Is he the greatest living painter in the United States?" The film is a look back into the life of an extraordinary man, a man who has fittingly been called "an artist dedicated to concealment, a celebrity who nobody knew." As he struggled with self-doubt, engaging in a lonely tug-of-war between needing to express himself and wanting to shut the world out, Pollock began a downward spiral.', 6.6, 8.483531, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/azsBSw2zw2uNHiCjTnbe9TJVEDB.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-EvqaHos7Oo'),
(3469, 15256, '200 Cigarettes', 'It''s 11:59 on New Years Eve... do you know where your date is?', 1999, 'A collection of twentysomethings try to cope with relationships, loneliness, desire and their individual neuroses.', 6.1, 3.561198, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/ssbx2Mk5ZCJWpXALuP2AdG0GFIT.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-ieEszV3TAU'),
(3470, 83686, 'The Words', 'There''s more than one way to take a life.', 2012, 'The Words follows young writer Rory Jansen who finally achieves long sought after literary success after publishing the next great American novel. There''s only one catch - he didn''t write it. As the past comes back to haunt him and his literary star continues to rise, Jansen is forced to confront the steep price that must be paid for stealing another man''s work, and for placing ambition and success above life''s most fundamental three words.', 6.4, 14.988746, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/aJtPLZS7tlpiQl6pEr8H42K565x.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lTlh70mx-eM'),
(3471, 80304, 'Casa De Mi Padre', 'Funniest movie you''ll ever read.', 2012, 'Scheming of a way to save their father''s ranch, the Alvarez brothers find themselves in a war with Mexico''s most feared drug lord.', 5.5, 5.754416, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/kVCc7xwTAlckBofazrwIz8x1TXC.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=01IYDy2Gdk4'),
(3472, 28053, 'City Island', 'Truth is stranger than family', 2009, 'The Rizzos, a family who doesn''t share their habits, aspirations, and careers with one another, find their delicate web of lies disturbed by the arrival of a young ex-con brought home by Vince, the patriarch of the family, who is a corrections officer in real life, and a hopeful actor in private.', 6.9, 6.497285, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/t7LJY2LCcGRLP9E4QbwBkLpZ2W7.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nkilMXjv0YE'),
(3473, 67913, 'The Guard', 'The FBI are about to discover that things work a little differently around here.', 2011, 'Two policemen must join forces to take on an international drug- smuggling gang - one, an unorthodox Irish policeman and the other, a straitlaced FBI agent. Sergeant Gerry Boyle is an eccentric small-town cop with a confrontational and crass personality and a subversive sense of humor. A longtime policeman in County Galway, Boyle is a maverick with his own moral code. He has seen enough of the world to know there isn''t much to it and has had plenty of time to think about it. When a fellow police officer disappears and Boyle''s small town becomes key to a large drug trafficking investigation, he is forced to at least feign interest when dealing with the humorless FBI agent Wendell Everett assigned to the case.', 6.8, 19.41114, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dtQiStID0le2EMTmJXupPRybARB.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iJxBKglv2zw'),
(3474, 13991, 'College', '', 2008, 'A wild weekend is in store for three high school seniors who visit a local college campus as prospective freshmen.', 4.8, 7.034618, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/e963mXIiuSwVyklsJxJ68mQ4CE.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_tv93-6uHl0'),
(3475, 1443, 'The Virgin Suicides', 'Beautiful, mysterious, haunting, invariably fatal. Just like life.', 1999, 'A group of male friends become obsessed with five mysterious sisters who are sheltered by their strict, religious parents.', 7.1, 26.218912, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1NCQtXPQnaHRjOZVmktA9BSM35F.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8kDcCGlaBwY'),
(3476, 8545, 'Little Voice', 'Finding your own voice can be magic.', 1998, 'After the death of her father, Little Voice or LV becomes a virtual recluse, never going out and hardly ever saying a word. She just sits in her bedroom listening to her father''s collection of old records of Shirley Bassey, Marilyn Monroe and various other famous female singers. But at night time, LV sings, imitating these great singers with surprising accuracy. One night she is overheard by one of her mother''s boyfriends, who happens to be a talent agent. He manages to convince her that her talent is special and arranges for her to perform at the local night club, but several problems arise.', 6.6, 4.647547, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7VxdMxSa3BEAvGl5nLvsgpBwrZH.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AqTaIbDTNnE'),
(3477, 19556, 'Miss March', 'After four years in a coma, Eugene Pratt is going to be reunited with his high school sweetheart... on pages 95-97.', 2009, 'A young man awakens from a four-year coma to hear that his once virginal high-school sweetheart has since become a centerfold in one of the world''s most famous men''s magazines. He and his sex-crazed best friend decide to take a cross-country road trip in order to crash a party at the magazine''s legendary mansion headquarters and win back the girl.', 5.4, 9.371534, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cWjaFmJ2pjMcWeKh00PJ3zOBMOq.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wk1_kDJhyBk'),
(3478, 231576, 'Wish I Was Here', 'Life is an occasion. Rise to it.', 2014, 'Aidan Bloom, a struggling actor, father and husband, is 35 years old and still trying to find a purpose for his life. He and his wife are barely getting by financially and Aidan passes his time by fantasizing about being the great futuristic Space-Knight he''d always dreamed he''d be as a little kid. When his ailing father can no longer afford to pay for private school for his two kids and the only available public school is on its last legs, Aidan reluctantly agrees to attempt to home-school them. Through teaching them about life his way, Aidan gradually discovers some of the parts of himself he couldn''t find.', 6.4, 15.015271, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hDDXIWLBS6rNPJS4tQvEXWxGXjK.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aCponfeWNOI'),
(3479, 16172, 'Simply Irresistible', 'Magic opened up their hearts... Love did the rest.', 1999, 'After her mother''s death, mediocre chef Amanda Shelton is having trouble attracting customers to her family''s restaurant. While shopping for ingredients, she is given a magical crab by mysterious Gene O''Reilly. Afterward, Amanda''s dishes suddenly become excellent, inducing strong emotional reactions in everyone who eats them. Tom Bartlett, who is preparing to open his own eatery, tries her cooking and falls in love.', 5.5, 5.696491, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zFsqqPQUz69wPaLBqQeiGbGiW7J.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MqV-bMYRZMw'),
(3480, 13403, 'Hedwig and the Angry Inch', 'An anatomically incorrect rock odyssey', 2001, 'A transexual punk rock girl from East Berlin tours the US with her rock band as she tells her life story and follows the ex-boyfriend/bandmate who stole her songs.', 7.4, 4.25422, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jafIFAW8sHQkzWPGoMDR4892dFI.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j9LxKv7ZkRo'),
(3481, 15797, 'Only the Strong', 'The ultimate martial art.', 1993, 'Former Green Beret Louis Stevens returns to his hometown of Miami after completing military service in Brazil, only to learn that his old high school has become a haven for gangs and drug dealers. After Stevens uses his capoeira skills to kick several drug dealers off of the school property, Kerrigan, one of Stevens'' old teachers, sees the impact that Stevens has on the students. Kerrigan gives him the task of teaching Capoeira to a handful of the worst at-risk students at the school.', 6.9, 5.411243, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pPWV5rBhCgzlzhwkpdRG7a7UZqt.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tJRLI_O9Reo'),
(3482, 347764, 'Goddess of Love', 'Be Careful Who You Get Close To', 2015, 'Enter into a baroque vortex of madness when an emotionally unstable woman is shattered after tremendous heartbreak. Brian was the love of Venus’ life and the thought of him having an affair with another woman begins her volatile descent into the dark side of psychosexual insanity.', 6.2, 1.273773, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5zrBskQtkPzthObgssDuUTG7hcd.jpg', NULL),
(3483, 13537, 'Shattered Glass', '', 2003, 'Fact-based 2003 drama about the young journalist Stephen Glass, who got a job at The New Republic in 1995 and for three years fabricated at least half of the stories he wrote.', 6.6, 6.27257, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1KHHNkrf8t15sXXF9d9TGq1T9jv.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Hrol_9rcBPs'),
(3484, 20794, 'Novocaine', '', 2001, 'A dentist finds himself a murder suspect after a sexy patient seduces him into prescribing her drugs', 6, 4.148253, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6ZVFepWKzYho4DLhyFVuRk7klZ1.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R3nyKA7N6to'),
(3485, 31064, 'The Business of Strangers', '', 2001, 'Julie Styron thinks she is going to be fired, but instead discovers that she is being promoted. Trapped in an airport hotel, she wants to celebrate but finds only the company of her young assistant, Paula Murphy. As the night progresses, the two women get to know each other. They flirt, they drink, they lie; personal flaws are revealed and exposed. But at the end of the night their relationship turns and becomes a complex battle of power, authority, and wit.', 5.7, 1.369649, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5iVwXnV2fraxy6NYzxZ07jMWW0u.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E9l6-x9o36w'),
(3486, 576, 'The Wild Bunch', 'If you only want to spend two hours in a movie theatre and go home and forget it, stay away from THE WILD BUNCH.', 1969, 'Aging outlaw Pike Bishop (William Holden) prepares to retire after one final robbery. Joined by his gang, which includes Dutch Engstrom (Ernest Borgnine) and brothers Lyle (Warren Oates) and Tector Gorch (Ben Johnson), Bishop discovers the heist is a setup orchestrated in part by his old partner, Deke Thornton (Robert Ryan). As the remaining gang takes refuge in Mexican territory, Thornton trails them, resulting in fierce gunfights with plenty of casualties', 7.6, 14.970654, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8j9yEC3xjy1PJDSizIbaxcHaSph.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kdy0t_8mQBw'),
(3487, 13990, 'The Wackness', '', 2008, 'Set in New York City in the sweltering summer, The Wackness tells the story of a troubled teenage drug dealer, who trades pot for therapy sessions with a drug-addled psychiatrist. Things get more complicated when he falls for one of his classmates, who just happens to be the doctors daughter. This is a coming-of-age story about sex, drugs, music and what it takes to be a man.', 6.2, 7.161051, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/gmtlqHZs8YBXcpMw4BgA3SGJfg8.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3VwN-KCpM6w'),
