(3591, 10987, 'Halloween: The Curse of Michael Myers', 'Haddonfield is ready to celebrate Halloween.... so is Michael Myers!', 1995, 'Six years ago, Michael Myers terrorized the town of Haddonfield, Illinois. He and his niece, Jamie Lloyd, have disappeared. Jamie was kidnapped by a bunch of evil druids who protect Michael Myers. And now, six years later, Jamie has escaped after giving birth to Michael''s child. She runs to Haddonfield to get Dr. Loomis to help her again.', 5, 9.483717, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/noCnM8nEI2bEDSdKHh0RKbwBwbC.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YZbc4LCDPsk'),
(3592, 1391, 'Y Tu Mamá También', 'Life has its ways of teaching. Life has its ways to confuse us. Life has its ways to move us. Life has its ways to amaze. Life has its ways to hurt us. Life has its ways to heal. Life has its ways to inspire.', 2001, 'In Mexico, two teenage boys and an attractive older woman embark on a road trip and learn a thing or two about life, friendship, sex, and each other.', 7.3, 16.890285, 'es', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/eTAQWIqHyFtnvNyYpFO5IoaVi1L.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=inc0vS58ZKg'),
(3593, 747, 'Shaun of the Dead', 'A romantic comedy. With zombies.', 2004, 'Shaun lives a supremely uneventful life, which revolves around his girlfriend, his mother, and, above all, his local pub. This gentle routine is threatened when the dead return to life and make strenuous attempts to snack on ordinary Londoners.', 7.5, 49.12486, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/dgXPhzNJH8HFTBjXPB177yNx6RI.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_QuY93B2FS0'),
(3594, 14745, 'The Haunting of Molly Hartley', 'Her past is yet to come.', 2008, 'When teenage Molly Hartley moves to a new town, she''s haunted by terrifying visions that may have to do with dark secrets from her past. Something evil lurks just beneath the lush surfaces of her private-school world, and it holds the rights to her very soul. On the eve of her 18th birthday, Molly is about to discover the truth of just who or what she is destined to become.', 4.3, 8.309894, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/XSy8BKHIa19yMAt7XyO2s9oIT5.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ka0BtFqv_xo'),
