(3980, 239, 'Some Like It Hot', 'The movie too HOT for words!', 1959, 'Two musicians witness a mob hit and struggle to find a way out of the city before they are found by the gangsters. Their only opportunity is to join an all-girl band as they leave on a tour. To make their getaway they must first disguise themselves as women, then keep their identities secret and deal with the problems this brings - such as an attractive bandmate and a very determined suitor.', 8, 39.30982, 'en', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hVIKyTK13AvOGv7ICmJjK44DTzp.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=97TYs2YXbJw'),
